name: Kazuma 1 (Shut-In No More)

quote_text: I'm sick of peddling street food. What do I do with these leftovers? So stressful!

quote_text: I've got a bottle of the good stuff stashed away. Wanna crack into it together?

quote_text: Verily, I say unto thee...the deity you worship is broke. Lend her some coin.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: Head over heels for me, eh? Gosh, I'm just too gorgeous for my own good.

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: Your favorite goddess could use a nice offering right about now.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: Life is full of regrets... So, take the easy route every chance you get, I say!

quote_text: Lia seems like a cool intellectual, but she's surprisingly passionate, too.

quote_text: I'm tired. Let's go back and have some bubbly!

quote_text: Everyone thinks too much. Just relax and go with the flow!

quote_text: What's the holdup, Kazuma? Need to use the bathroom?

quote_text: I'm happy to save people in need, but that doesn't apply to the undead!

quote_text: I can eat and drink as much as I like. Goddesses don't gain weight!

quote_text: Lia's room is a total mess. It's well beyond even my powers of purification.

quote_text: Seeing as it's your favorite goddess's birthday, I'll take an offering of bubbly brew, thank you very much!

name: Megumin 1 (Explosive)

name: Megumin 2 (Magical Melodrama)

quote_text: That's a lot of snow sprites. Let's take 'em down and cash in!

quote_text: The world has shunned me for my calamitous might. Be you brave enough to take this terrible weight upon your party?

name: Megumin 2 (Arch Wizard)
quote_text: I've been investing all my skill points in one spell and one spell alone: Explosion.

quote_text: Nothing beats a good rest every once in a while.

name: Megumin 2 (Day Off)
quote_text: The weather's perfect...for a heaping helping of explosion magic!

quote_text: I'll do anything! I'll even lug your...er, luggage! Just PLEASE keep me around!

quote_text: Now! I will blast away our foes with my explosion magic!

name: Megumin 2 (Explosive Devotion)
quote_text: I'm the better mage, so I'll never let Yunyun get the better of me!

quote_text: Time for some karuta. As a member of the Crimson Demon Clan, I shall not lose!

name: Megumin 2 (Legendary Adventurer)

quote_text: Birthdays... Grand occasions to be celebrated in explosive fashion. So behold, my most potent explosion yet!

quote_text: A crusader never leaves anyone behind... Oh, the sweet suffering!

name: Darkness 2 (Human Shield)
quote_text: I'll fight 'til I fall! You stay outta harm's way!

name: Darkness 2 (Winter Layers)
quote_text: My strength and durability are second to none. But when it comes to offense...I can't hit a thing.

quote_text: To a crusader, the quest is everything.

name: Darkness 2 (Crusader)

quote_text: S-strip me down, will you? You sick, twisted animal...!

quote_text: Use me as a shield. No, please...I insist.

quote_text: Let me know if you ever think I'm holding the party back. In fact, chew me the heck out!

name: Darkness 2 (True Knight)

quote_text: Having my clothes slowly shredded by tooth and claw... Ooh!

name: Darkness 2 (Extension Request)
quote_text: Sneaking into beds at night... What a tricky monster.

quote_text: It's time for our Christmas gifts! If there's anything you want, just ask.

name: Darkness 2 (Secret Present)
quote_text: Delivering presents to kids while they sleep? Christmas is a wonderful holiday!

name: Darkness 1 (Crusader's Spirit)
quote_text: Using a calligraphy brush is rather difficult. This is my first time writing on the floor, too.

name: Darkness 2 (Crusader's Spirit)
quote_text: My New Year's resolution is to protect everyone as a crusader. Use me as much as you like!

quote_text: Even if my body crumbles, I will never bend to evil!

name: Darkness 2 (Legendary Adventurer)

name: Darkness 2 (Sword Princess's Student)
quote_text: Ais is an amazing teacher of swordplay, especially when she lands a hit on me!

name: Darkness 1 (Girlish Pursuits)
quote_text: Hmm-mmm... What am I doing, you ask? Isn't it obvious? I'm knitting!

name: Darkness 2 (Girlish Pursuits)
quote_text: I'm a woman too, you know! It hurts when people say my muscles are rock-hard or that I'm freakishly strong!

name: Darkness (Expectant Gaze) 1
quote_text: D-Devil King, why did you ask me to wear such an unladylike outfit?!

name: Darkness (Expectant Gaze) 2
quote_text: Hmph. You have to hand it to Albedo to be totally comfortable in such an outfit.

quote_text: I'm not much of a chef, so please walk me through it!

name: Darkness (Passionate Pastry Chef) 2
quote_text: I don't understand! I wanted to make chocolates, not this mud pie!

name: Darkness 1 (Mysterious Adventurer)
quote_text: No matter who my opponent is, my mission remains the same… Bring it on. I am the wall!

name: Darkness 2 (Mysterious Adventurer)
quote_text: Typical Kazuma, always comes up with ridiculous ideas.

name: Darkness 1 (Chatting with Friend)
quote_text: I'm lightly dressed now but I'm a crusader… Don't hold back and give your strongest hit!

name: Darkness 2 (Chatting with Friend)
quote_text:
Being with Chris makes me comfortable.
It's another different kind than being with the party.

quote_text: I always wanted to be covered in slime, it feels good.

name: ASSET_CHARA_VOICE_306103040
quote_text: Me all covered in slime… Is a turn on?!

quote_text: All the crowd's eyes are on me….Ugh!

name: Darkness 2 (Masochism Rapper)
quote_text: I know it's the unit name, but please don't call me Lalatina!

quote_text: Do I not like pain? I rather like it too much!

name: Darkness 2 (Direct Hit)
quote_text: A big shield… Sure is reliable, but why I do I feel so sad!

quote_text: Today… is Valentine’s Day, and I have something I want to give you.

name: Darkness 2 (Hidden Heart)
quote_text: I-It doesn't mean anything special! I'm just trying to express my gratitude.

quote_text: I can't believe I can look down at the village from such a high place… It feels like a dream.

name: Darkness 2 (Beautiful Night View)
quote_text: This world's night view is truly beautiful. It's like a shining jewel box.

quote_text: It’s no use trying to make me give in. I will never kneel... Never!

name: Darkness (Rising Delusion) 2
quote_text: If Slimes attack me while I’m in such a vulnerable state... Ugh!

quote_text: I never knew the light reflected on the night beach could be so beautiful...

name: Darkness (In The Brilliant Light) 2
quote_text: H-How does Kazuma know my swimsuit size?!

name: Darkness (Fantastic Adventurer) 1
quote_text: Right now... I look like a hell hound.

name: Darkness (Fantastic Adventurer) 2
quote_text: You want me to wag my tail with my belly in the air like a dog?! Of course I will...!

name: Darkness (Satisfying Battle) 1
quote_text: Axel's Angel Squad... W-What kind of brutal treatment did you give me?!

name: Darkness (Satisfying Battle) 2
quote_text: *Sigh*... I’m satisfied... W-Wait, you don't have to carry me! Let me just roll on the ground like now!

quote_text: Running and dragging a heavy sleigh through the town during this cold weather... I'm getting chills from just thinking about it!

name: Darkness (Tempted Reindeer) 2
quote_text: You want me to wear this beast-like outfit and run around town?! What a fresh reward!

name: Darkness 1 (Hot Water)
quote_text: L-let go of the towel! If you tug, I swear...!

name: Darkness 2 (Hot Water)
quote_text: Can you not stare? It's kind of embarrassing.

name: Darkness 3 (Hot Water)
quote_text: This is NOT battle attire!

name: Darkness 4 (Hot Water)
quote_text: Towel... STAY ON!

name: Darkness 5 (Hot Water)
quote_text: H-hey, no staring!

name: Darkness 6 (Hot Water)
quote_text: Fighting isn't half-bad!

name: Darkness 1 (Girl's Night)
quote_text: It's nice to enjoy a quiet drink every once in a while.

name: Darkness 2 (Girl's Night)
quote_text: If you can't sleep, would you like to join me for a little chat?

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: Let's go on a quest with extra brutal, hard-hitting, freaky-deaky monsters!

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: It's an honor to join your party.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: N-never call me Lalatina! Never ever!

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: Vassals and commoners may flee, but a true knight remains ever steadfast.

quote_text: Forced to grovel, face thrust into the ground... There is no greater reward!

quote_text: No ally of mine has a smile that innocent! Come, show me your inner scumbag!

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: It's the duty of a lady knight to be taken by the Devil King's sadistic lackeys.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: I have no doubt that the Devil King's underlings will do unspeakable things to me.

quote_text: If you have a problem with my performance, you need only chastise me. Don't hold back!

quote_text: Oh, woe is me! This is the height of shame! Yes, oh, yes!

name: Wiz 3 (Water Blast)
quote_text: I feel a bit embarrassed.

name: Wiz 4 (Water Blast)
quote_text: I'm going to melt in this heat!

name: Wiz 5 (Water Blast)
quote_text: The sea breeze feels so good.

name: Wiz 6 (Water Blast)
quote_text: Could you rub some sunscreen on me?

name: Wiz 1 (Christmas Eve)
quote_text: That's a wonderful Christmas tree. I bet my customers would love it.

name: Wiz 2 (Christmas Eve)
quote_text: To think, Princess Iris is attending too. This will be a Christmas party for the ages.

name: Wiz 3 (Christmas Eve)
quote_text: Let's put on a Christmas sale.

name: Wiz 4 (Christmas Eve)
quote_text: It would be so wonderful if it snowed.

name: Wiz 5 (Christmas Eve)
quote_text: Merry Christmas!

name: Wiz 6 (Christmas Eve)
quote_text: The chicken's ready to eat!

name: Battle 39
quote_text: Cursed Petrification!

name: Battle 40
quote_text: No holding back!

name: Wiz 1 (Fancy Dress)
quote_text: Kazuma said these clothes are every man's dream... What did he mean by that?

name: Wiz 2 (Fancy Dress)
quote_text: Mia really knows how to bring customers into the shop.

name: Wiz 3 (Fancy Dress)
quote_text: This outfit makes it hard to move around!

name: Wiz 4 (Fancy Dress)
quote_text: I feel different, like a new me.

name: Wiz 5 (Fancy Dress)
quote_text: Try some, if you'd like.

name: Wiz 6 (Fancy Dress)
quote_text: Um, I don't really need to change— Hey, wait!

name: Wiz 1 (Bumbling Bunny Girl)
quote_text: The owner scolded me again... It's pretty hard working at a casino.

name: Wiz 2 (Bumbling Bunny Girl)
quote_text: Do you think I should dress up as a bunny to greet customers at my shop?

name: Wiz 3 (Bumbling Bunny Girl)
quote_text: Place your bets!

name: Wiz 4 (Bumbling Bunny Girl)
quote_text: Umm... This is sort of embarrassing...

name: Wiz 5 (Bumbling Bunny Girl)
quote_text: That was quite fun!

name: Wiz 6 (Bumbling Bunny Girl)
quote_text: On to the next challenge.

name: Battle 41
quote_text: Here I come!

name: Battle 42
quote_text: Is this sufficient?

name: Battle 43
quote_text: That helps a little.

name: Wiz 1 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Sorry! I'm really sorry! I don't know if I'm worthy of such a legendary yukata.

name: Wiz 2 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: This outfit reminds me of my days as an adventurer.

name: Wiz 3 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: They used to call me the "Ice Witch."

name: Wiz 4 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: This brings back so many memories...

name: Wiz 5 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Rest in everlasting peace.

name: Wiz 6 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Excuse me, please let me through.

name: Wiz (Gorgeous New Year) 1
quote_text: Wiz's shop will have loads of incredible magic items for everyone again this year!

name: Wiz (Gorgeous New Year) 2
quote_text: I love how a kimono looks. It is a little tight in the chest area though...

name: Wiz (Gorgeous New Year) 3
quote_text: We hope to see you at the shop this year too!

name: Wiz (Gorgeous New Year) 4
quote_text: We've plenty of special New Year's deals!

name: Wiz (Gorgeous New Year) 5
quote_text: Our decorations look amazing!

name: Wiz (Gorgeous New Year) 6
quote_text: New Year's is here once again!

name: Wiz 1 (No Relaxing)
quote_text: Hot springs are really nice. *sigh*… So relaxing....

name: Wiz 2 (No Relaxing)
quote_text: Umm… since we're in a hot spring, why don't we just quietly relax?

name: Wiz 3 (No Relaxing)
quote_text: Should we go in the tub?

name: Wiz 4 (No Relaxing)
quote_text: Relax yourself.

name: Wiz 5 (No Relaxing)
quote_text: I feel warm and cozy. The hot spring was nice.

name: Wiz 6 (No Relaxing)
quote_text: Let's stay hydrated.

name: Wiz 1 (Forbidden Adventurer)
quote_text: You didn't forget that I was an Arch Wizard, right?

name: Wiz 2 (Forbidden Adventurer)
quote_text: There's nothing you can do about adventurers being hunted. Since they would have been ready for it.

name: Wiz 3 (Forbidden Adventurer)
quote_text: With… this forbidden power…

name: Wiz 4 (Forbidden Adventurer)
quote_text: Dangerous power comes at a price.

name: Wiz 5 (Forbidden Adventurer)
quote_text: Is this hope or a catastrophe…

name: Wiz 6 (Forbidden Adventurer)
quote_text: It feels kind of empty to win all the time.

name: Wiz 7 (Forbidden Adventurer)
quote_text: Forbidden Cursed Necromancy!

name: Wiz 8 (Forbidden Adventurer)
quote_text: Give me strength!

name: Wiz 1 (Unstoppable Shopping)
quote_text: There are so many things in this world. I will make note of it for the future!

name: Wiz 2 (Unstoppable Shopping)
quote_text: Take a look at this. All these brilliant things. I want to sell them in my shop!

name: Wiz (Frozen Magic) 1
quote_text: Happy New Year. I'm not used to wearing such a beautiful dress, how do I look?

name: Wiz (Frozen Magic) 2
quote_text: This party hall, decorated with ice sculptures, is wonderful. I want to put them in my shop as well.

name: Wiz 3 (Unstoppable Shopping)
quote_text: Give me everything on that shelf!

name: Wiz 4 (Unstoppable Shopping)
quote_text: I can't pass up such a cheap price!

name: Wiz 5 (Unstoppable Shopping)
quote_text: I’m so satisfied after buying so many things!

name: Wiz 6 (Unstoppable Shopping)
quote_text: Let’s go to that antique shop next!

name: Wiz (Frozen Magic) 3
quote_text: It's an honor to be invited.

name: Wiz (Frozen Magic) 4
quote_text: It's been a while since I've worn such a beautiful dress.

name: Wiz (Frozen Magic) 5
quote_text: To celebrate the victory... Cheers.

name: Wiz (Frozen Magic) 6
quote_text: May it never stop even in the new year...!

name: Wiz 6 (Sweet Dreams)
quote_text: Quiet, please. Everyone is tired.

name: Wiz 1 (Bunny Buddy)
quote_text: This magical item will let you befriend bunnies.

name: Wiz 2 (Bunny Buddy)
quote_text: They may be a bit embarrassing, but I highly recommend them.

name: Wiz 1 (Way of the Kunoichi)
quote_text: L-Like this? Being a kunoichi is hard work.

name: Wiz 2 (Way of the Kunoichi)
quote_text: Um, Arue? How long are we going to work on victory poses?

name: Wiz 1 (Baking With Chocolate)
quote_text: I'll bake you some delicious chocolates to show you my gratitude.

name: Wiz 2 (Baking With Chocolate)
quote_text: T-Teaching the princess how to make chocolate? I'm a little nervous!

name: Wiz 1 (Stinging Sensation)
quote_text: Lady Aqua's tears sting... I'm vanishing! I'm starting to vanish!

name: Wiz 2 (Stinging Sensation)
quote_text: There, there... It's all right now. So you can stop crying...

name: Wiz (Lich Protector) 1
quote_text: You'll never get your hands on the best magic items without taking some risks!

name: Wiz (Lich Protector) 2
quote_text: I am an excellent judge of a product's quality. Leave it to me.

name: Wiz 1 (Summer Beach)
quote_text: The flames are beautiful… I also love how they fade away.

name: Wiz 2 (Summer Beach)
quote_text: Let's enjoy tonight and start doing our best tomorrow!

name: Wiz 1 (Holy Night’s Stock)
quote_text: Ugh… The shop will be at risk if I don’t sell everything at all costs…!

name: Wiz 2 (Holy Night’s Stock)
quote_text: C-Calm down, Vanir…! We will be able to sell everything!

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: Sure I'll help. After all, I used to be an adventuring arch wizard myself.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: Oh, did I not tell you? I used to be one of the Devil King's generals.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: Why is my store always in the red? I just don't get it...

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: I just got some new items in. Would you like to take a look?

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: No purification spells, please. I'll vanish into thin air.

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: I-I am NOT a "sorry shopkeeper"!

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: Ditch work? No, no...Vanir will have my head!

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: Recommended items? Well...this crystal strengthens friendship. Try it with me?

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: If the going gets tough on a quest, let me know. I'll shower you in items.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: Mind if I...borrow some of your magic power?

name: Greeting
quote_text: I run a magic shop in town.

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: Always happy to help!

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: You're such a kind soul. Thank you.

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: It's time to order some new stock.

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: Business will be booming before long!

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: Sorry, sorry, sorry! So very, very sorry!

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: I am not inhuman...I'm just a little less alive!

name: Battle 1
quote_text: I'll take you on!

name: Battle 2
quote_text: I hope the shop's okay...

name: Battle 3
quote_text: That's the way!

name: Battle 4
quote_text: Stop by the shop anytime!

name: Battle 5
quote_text: I botched that one...

name: Battle 6
quote_text: Being immortal doesn't make me hate losing any less.

name: Battle 7
quote_text: Hyah!

name: Battle 8
quote_text: Sorry...

name: Battle 9
quote_text: Behold the power of a lich!

name: Battle 10
quote_text: This will sting a little.

name: Battle 11
quote_text: Be right there!

name: Battle 12
quote_text: I don't mean to be soi dense, really!

name: Battle 13
quote_text: I won't hold back!

name: Battle 14
quote_text: Yeek!

name: Battle 15
quote_text: Yeeeeeek!

name: Battle 16
quote_text: All set to go!

name: Battle 17
quote_text: This enemy's no joke.

name: Battle 18
quote_text: Uh oh, uh oh!

name: Battle 19
quote_text: Shall we, then?

name: Battle 20
quote_text: I used to be an adventurer, you know.

name: Battle 21
quote_text: Please go easy on me.

name: Battle 22
quote_text: Why don't you take a breather in my shop?

name: Battle 23
quote_text: Look, Vanir! I won!

name: Battle 24
quote_text: Until next time.

name: Battle 25
quote_text: Sorry! I'm sorry!

name: Battle 26
quote_text: Hyah!

name: Battle 27
quote_text: Hraaaaaah!

name: Battle 28
quote_text: Prepare yourself!

name: Battle 29
quote_text: I'll make this painless.

name: Battle 30
quote_text: I beg your pardon!

name: Battle 31
quote_text: I can still do this!

name: Battle 32
quote_text: Cursed Crystal Prison!

name: Battle 33
quote_text: Aaahhh!

name: Battle 34
quote_text: I see someone over there...

name: Battle 35
quote_text: Let's end this here!

name: Battle 36
quote_text: I'm vanishing!

name: Battle 37
quote_text: Did I do that?!

name: Battle 38
quote_text: I want to live up to everyone's expectations!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: I assure you, my heart's still human.

name: Misc 2
quote_text: I'm so happy I could just...vanish!

name: Misc 3
quote_text: Ooh, a customer! Welcome.

name: Misc 4
quote_text: I provide quality items for all.

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Yes, I was a Devil King Army Commander. But my only job was maintaining the castle walls.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: I will not tolerate the killing of innocent people!

name: Misc 7
quote_text: How can I work so hard, yet be so poor? It's baffling...

name: Misc 8
quote_text: Lady Aqua?! When you touch me, it burns... Owww!

name: Misc 9
quote_text: The items Kazuma came up with are selling quite well.

name: Misc 10
quote_text: Amy and Mia seem like real sisters.

name: Misc 11
quote_text: I wonder how we can increase our sales?

name: Misc 12
quote_text: We have Axel Hearts photo prints for sale!

name: Misc 13
quote_text: We need to think up some new products! Got any ideas?

name: Misc 14
quote_text: I'm sure this product will sell. I recommend it, after all!

name: Misc 15
quote_text: Liches don't need to sleep, but we do get tired if we stay up all night.

name: Misc 16
quote_text: We're in the red again. But how? I'm working really hard.

name: Misc 17
quote_text: If I had a little sister like Mia, I think I'd be more responsible.

name: Misc 18
quote_text: Cielo is one of my regular customers. She buys lots of gloves.

name: Misc 19
quote_text: Vanir, please stop acting like you'll use your Death Ray!

name: Misc 20
quote_text: Amy and Mia always drop by the store together.

name: Misc 21
quote_text: Vanir keeps telling me he can run the store! But it's mine!

name: Misc 22
quote_text: Sorry! I'm really sorry! A lich shouldn't live in such luxury!

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: How did I become a lich? Hehehe, I'll tell you some other time.

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: Um... Vanir? Why do you look like you're about to use your Death Ray on me?

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: I find talking with Amy to really be quite soothing.

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: We have several of Kazuma's inventions for sale.

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: We have Vanir dolls that ward off evil. Unfortunately, they laugh all night long.

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: I'd very much like to open a shop in another town one day.

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: Our Axel Hearts' merch is flying off the shelves lately!

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: Melissa is one of our best customers. Just the other day, she sold me a priceless artifact...

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: I need a long dip in a hot bath. It's a shame there aren't any hot springs in Axel...

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: If you come across any rare items, you know where to bring them!

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: This reminds me of my days as an adventurer. It's exciting.

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: I'm happy that I can overcome these trials, but why am I still so bad at running my shop?

name: Game Title 1
quote_text: God's Blessing on this Wonderful World! Fantastic Days

name: Game Title 2
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Game Title 3
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Yunyun 1 (Megumin's Friend)
quote_text: Hey, Megumin, s-stop! You win, okay?

name: Yunyun 2 (Megumin's Friend)
quote_text: Hey, that's a little close for comfort! Though...does this makes us look like friends?

name: Yunyun 1 (Seeking Friends)
quote_text: Say, do you wanna be f-frien... Nevermind!

name: Yunyun 2 (Seeking Friends)
quote_text: They say hotpot tastes better when sharing it with friends. Someday, Yunyun, someday...

name: Yunyun 1 (Arch Wizard)
quote_text: There’s no way I'm letting HER beat me!

name: Yunyun 2 (Arch Wizard)
quote_text: I know intermediate and advanced magic like the back of my hand!

name: Yunyun 1 (Crimson Demon)
quote_text: Someday, I'll be clan chief!

name: Yunyun 2 (Crimson Demon)
quote_text: The Crimson Demon Village has quite a few sightseeing spots.

name: Yunyun 1 (Beginner)
quote_text: I hope I can make a bunch of friends.

name: Yunyun 2 (Beginner)
quote_text: Playing chess alone is actually pretty fun. No, really.

name: Yunyun 1 (Wakey Wakey)
quote_text: The pajama party... I must have fallen asleep.

name: Yunyun 2 (Wakey Wakey)
quote_text: It was...a dream? But I made so many friends...

name: Yunyun 1 (Grand Performance)
quote_text: "Oh please, Mr. Hero! Save me from the Devil King!"

name: Yunyun 2 (Grand Performance)
quote_text: Should I add more emotion? Or would that feel too unnatural?

name: Yunyun 1 (Magic Academy Memories)
quote_text: This takes me back to my school days. Ahh, memories...

name: Yunyun 2 (Magic Academy Memories)
quote_text: I wish I could've eaten lunch and walked to school with my friends.

name: Yunyun 1 (Beachcomber)
quote_text: I-I'm not lonely! It's easier to build sandcastles on my own!

name: Yunyun 2 (Beachcomber)
quote_text: This sandcastle turned out better than expected. I'll challenge Megumin next!

name: Yunyun 1 (Perfect Fit)
quote_text: My uniform seems smaller than Megumin's...

name: Yunyun 2 (Perfect Fit)
quote_text: I-I am Yunyun! Server of...th-the best coffee in all of Axel!

name: Yunyun 1 (Friendly Halloween)
quote_text: Trick-or-treat! W-Would you mind if we celebrated together?

name: Yunyun 2 (Friendly Halloween)
quote_text: What a wonderful day to spend with friends. I wish it was always Halloween!

name: Yunyun 1 (Bath Battle)
quote_text: Accept my challenge if you dare, Megumin! Being we're at a hot spring, let's see who's more devel— Hey, are you listening?!

name: Yunyun 2 (Bath Battle)
quote_text: H-How would you like to chat after we finish in the hot springs? I bought some Arcanretian cake!

name: Yunyun 1 (Rival's Pride)
quote_text: Have a taste of Crimson Demon magic! Light of Saber!

name: Yunyun 2 (Rival's Pride)
quote_text: These monsters are nothing for the future leader of our clan!

name: Yunyun 1 (Studious Sister)
quote_text: Are you really still sleeping? You're going to be late, you know.

name: Yunyun 2 (Studious Sister)
quote_text: All I want is a friend who I can study with, walk to school with, and join an afterschool club with...

name: Yunyun 1 (Summer Fireworks)
quote_text: Going to the festival with everyone and watching fireworks in the garden... I never thought I could be so happy!

name: Yunyun 2 (Summer Fireworks)
quote_text: A night sky bursting with rings of explosion magic... Summer in the Crimson Demon Village is truly special.

name: Yunyun (My Feast!) 1
quote_text: Ugh... I know it's Christmas, but why do I have to let Megumin eat my food?

name: Yunyun (My Feast!) 2
quote_text: Alone on Christmas? That'd be awful! Fortunately, I've got plenty of friends to spend it with this year!

name: Yunyun (Fervent Wisher) 1
quote_text: P-Please be my friend! Even if it's only for New Year's!

name: Yunyun (Fervent Wisher) 2
quote_text: I'm really good at karuta! I even practice alone!

name: Yunyun 1 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: My name is Yunyun! Magic power suited for a Crimson Demon chief in my hands!

name: Yunyun 2 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: This may be a little too much for me, but may be I can beat Megumin with this…?

name: Yunyun 1 (Rookie Judgement)
quote_text: Judge, judgement!

name: Yunyun 2 (Rookie Judgement)
quote_text: I will n…not forgive those threaten the peace of this town!

name: Yunyun 1 (Oasis Shelter)
quote_text: I wanna rest a little longer here by the water….

name: Yunyun 2 (Oasis Shelter)
quote_text: What a place in the middle of the desert… Maybe a little break here?

name: Yunyun 1 (Borrowing Race)
quote_text: I brought a whole roasted big for the Halloween party….

name: Yunyun 2 (Borrowing Race)
quote_text: There are a lot of goods left. We can play all we want with them!

name: Yunyun 1 (Lonely Karuta)
quote_text: Would Karuta be fun to play alone?

name: Yunyun 2 (Lonely Karuta)
quote_text: The next match with Megumin will be decided with Karuta!

name: Yunyun 1 (High-speed Tea Cup)
quote_text: Wait, Megumin! Come on, I want to take my time looking around while we’re here.

name: Yunyun 2 (High-speed Tea Cup)
quote_text: W-What should I do?! I got swept up by the crowd and came to an unfamiliar place…!

name: Yunyun 1 (Crimson Demon Miko)
quote_text: Welcome to the Cat Ears Shrine.

name: Yunyun 2 (Crimson Demon Miko)
quote_text: When I clean the shrine, I feel moew-y heart also being cleaned... *Gasp*!

name: Yunyun (A Case Awaits) 1
quote_text: Huff, huff... Being a detective needs a lot more stamina than I thought...

name: Yunyun (A Case Awaits) 2
quote_text: A member of the detectives club is basically a friend, right?

name: Yunyun (Forbidden Adventurer) 1
quote_text: The only one that listens to my voice is just... the Void.

name: Yunyun (Forbidden Adventurer) 2
quote_text: Only the cold cage and the endless silence, comfort my heart...

name: Yunyun (New Year Together) 1
quote_text: H-Happy New Year! It's awesome to celebrate New Year's Day in a castle...!

name: Yunyun (New Year Together) 2
quote_text: The ice mansion from the party, I want to visit it with my friends...!

name: Yunyun (New Member?) 1
quote_text: If I join the Shadow Garden, will I make a bunch of friends...?!

name: Yunyun (New Member?) 2
quote_text: Although it's very comfortable to move around in this outfit, Megumin's gaze is bothering me...

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: It is I, the feared Yunyun! Master arch wizard and wielder of advanced magic!

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: Not all Crimson Demons are show-offs!

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: You'd let ME in your party? Pinch me, I must be dreaming...

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: Someday, I'll settle my rivalry with Megumin!

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: I'd be friends with anyone. I mean, even a monster would be okay...

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: Huh? I'd almost say we're acting like...friends?

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: People tend to write Dust off as riff-raff, but he's actually pretty nice.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: Grab a bite to eat? I'm buying!

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: I wonder how Funifura and Dodonko are doing back home?

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: W-would you want to...take a trip somewhere? F-friends do that sorta thing, right?

name: Greeting
quote_text: Oh, didn't expect to meet you here! What a coincidence. B-because that's what it is!

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: At this rate, I'll definitely make a name for myself someday!

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: I'm the daughter of the Crimson Demon chieftain!

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: I'm more than capable of pulling through alone!

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: I won't let Megumin take the lead!

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: No trial is too much for the future leader of the Crimson Demons!

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: This new power will give me the advantage over Megumin!

name: Battle 1
quote_text: It's on.

name: Battle 2
quote_text: Witness the power of a Crimson Demon!

name: Battle 3
quote_text: Er, uh... Want to be friends?

name: Battle 4
quote_text: Let's all grab a bite together.

name: Battle 5
quote_text: One more contest. Just one!

name: Battle 6
quote_text: That's the last time I lose. You'll see.

name: Battle 7
quote_text: I'm stronger than I look!

name: Battle 8
quote_text: Let's go!

name: Battle 9
quote_text: Say your prayers!

name: Battle 10
quote_text: Let an expert handle this!

name: Battle 11
quote_text: Stay sharp, everyone!

name: Battle 12
quote_text: I won't be beaten!

name: Battle 13
quote_text: Behold, i-it is I...the great Yunyun!

name: Battle 14
quote_text: Yow!

name: Battle 15
quote_text: I miss my village...

name: Battle 16
quote_text: Show me what you've got!

name: Battle 17
quote_text: Yeowch...

name: Battle 18
quote_text: Call me when you need me.

name: Battle 19
quote_text: I can't let everyone down!

name: Battle 20
quote_text: I-I'll be your opponent!

name: Battle 21
quote_text: My name is Yunyun! It's time to fight!

name: Battle 22
quote_text: If I win, then will you...

name: Battle 23
quote_text: I hope we can quest together again soon.

name: Battle 24
quote_text: I can't believe I lost!

name: Battle 25
quote_text: It's all my fault.

name: Battle 26
quote_text: Take that!

name: Battle 27
quote_text: I'm sorry!

name: Battle 28
quote_text: I am not a loner!

name: Battle 29
quote_text: Take this!

name: Battle 30
quote_text: I-I've got to save my friends!

name: Battle 31
quote_text: Of course I would help them!

name: Battle 32
quote_text: Light of Saber!

name: Battle 33
quote_text: Yeek!

name: Battle 34
quote_text: I'll show you all next time!

name: Battle 35
quote_text: All set to go!

name: Battle 36
quote_text: I can't go on...

name: Battle 37
quote_text: Have I been forgotten?!

name: Battle 38
quote_text: Looks like it's my turn.

name: Yunyun 3 (Magic Academy Memories)
quote_text: Huh? My uniform has gotten so tight!

name: Yunyun 4 (Magic Academy Memories)
quote_text: This reminds me of my school days.

name: Yunyun 5 (Magic Academy Memories)
quote_text: I love wearing my uniform outside of school.

name: Yunyun 6 (Magic Academy Memories)
quote_text: I'd like a do-over on my school days.

name: Yunyun 3 (Friendly Halloween)
quote_text: H-Happy Halloween!

name: Yunyun 4 (Friendly Halloween)
quote_text: Good friends are better than tasty snacks.

name: Yunyun 5 (Friendly Halloween)
quote_text: Halloween sure is fun...

name: Yunyun 6 (Friendly Halloween)
quote_text: H-How about a treat?!

name: Yunyun 3 (Bath Battle)
quote_text: Can I really fight dressed like this?

name: Yunyun 4 (Bath Battle)
quote_text: Before we get cold!

name: Yunyun 5 (Bath Battle)
quote_text: Let's get in the hot spring!

name: Yunyun 6 (Bath Battle)
quote_text: I-Is this towel all right?

quote_text: Ooh! Is this a reward for my little "art project" at the Eris church?

name: Battle 1
quote_text: You can't beat the world's prettiest priest!

name: Battle 2
quote_text: There are two things I can't stand: evildoers and Eris followers!

name: Battle 3
quote_text: How 'bout a toast with some delicious jelly slime?

name: Battle 4
quote_text: Another productive day at work!

name: Battle 5
quote_text: Surely I could have picked an easier job...

name: Battle 6
quote_text: I'm not wrong! Everyone else is!

name: Battle 7
quote_text: The goddess Eris pads her chest!

name: Battle 8
quote_text: Hraaagh!

name: Battle 9
quote_text: I shall bury the enemies of the Order!

name: Battle 10
quote_text: Help! Perv on the loose!

name: Battle 11
quote_text: May Lady Aqua's blessing go with you.

name: Battle 12
quote_text: Well? Feel like joining the Order?

name: Battle 13
quote_text: You're not an Axis disciple? Tsk, tsk.

name: Battle 14
quote_text: Yeek!

name: Battle 15
quote_text: The Order of Axis is eternal!

name: Battle 16
quote_text: Praise be Lady Aqua, our benevolent goddess!

name: Battle 17
quote_text: Such a brute!

name: Battle 18
quote_text: Don't forget about me.

name: Battle 19
quote_text: Blessed by the Order of Axis!

name: Battle 20
quote_text: Very well. I will help if I must!

name: Battle 21
quote_text: Someone to pamper me?!

name: Battle 22
quote_text: My prayers have been answered!

name: Battle 23
quote_text: I must receive my serving of bread!

name: Battle 24
quote_text: You will not get away with this!

name: Battle 25
quote_text: A young woman shouldn't be this sad...

name: Battle 26
quote_text: I'll give you the surprise of a lifetime!

name: Battle 27
quote_text: Gotcha!

name: Battle 28
quote_text: Where are the cute girls?

name: Battle 29
quote_text: Defeat the Devil King! Strike down the Devil King!

name: Battle 30
quote_text: Long live the Order of Axis!

name: Battle 31
quote_text: The teachings of the Order of Axis are the way of truth!

name: Battle 32
quote_text: Axis Attack!

name: Battle 33
quote_text: Kyah!

name: Battle 34
quote_text: This is the fault of those who follow the Eris faith.

name: Battle 35
quote_text: Have I got a surprise for you!

name: Battle 36
quote_text: I despise difficult things!

name: Battle 37
quote_text: Have you been enchanted by my beauty?

name: Battle 38
quote_text: Just sign here to join!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: Hehe. Now that's a line I've never heard.

name: Misc 2
quote_text: I like you a lot. Maybe as much as delicious jelly slime, even!

name: Misc 3
quote_text: Just between us... Axis-brand detergent is so safe, you can drink it!

name: Misc 4
quote_text: I'll protect you from those sinister Eris disciples.

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Ever heard of Cecily, Axel's prettiest priest? Yep, that's me!

name: Misc 6
quote_text: Now, how should I rile up those Eris phonies today?

name: Misc 7
quote_text: Hee hee hee. Any teeny-tiny cutesy-wootsies in need of a big sis today?

name: Misc 8
quote_text: I'll spread the word of the Order of Axis throughout Axel!

name: Misc 9
quote_text: How about a date with the poster girl for the Order of Axis?

name: Misc 10
quote_text: Lady Aqua teaches us to enjoy the now, not an unknown future.

name: Misc 11
quote_text: I want Megumin and Komekko to sandwich me in a great big hug.

name: Misc 12
quote_text: Yunyun, there are friends waiting for you in the Order of Axis!

name: Misc 13
quote_text: Darkness just won't convert. Guess I have to try harder!

name: Misc 14
quote_text: Want to go with me and get free bread from the Eris faith?

name: Misc 15
quote_text: Long live the Order of Axis! All together now! Don't be shy!

name: Misc 16
quote_text: Sign this form and I'll let you treat me to dinner!

name: Misc 17
quote_text: Everyone is either in the Order of Axis or wants to be in it!

name: Misc 18
quote_text: If you join the Order of Axis, you'll get free soap that you can even eat.

name: Misc 19
quote_text: Wait up, handsome! I've chosen you to be my future husband!

name: Misc 20
quote_text: *Yawn* I had a dream of an amazing jelly slime bath.

name: Misc 21
quote_text: Do you think Axel Hearts will help me spread the word?

name: Misc 22
quote_text: Those Eris heretics need a little punishment, wouldn't you agree?

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: Megumin is the most adorable little thing!

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: Help! Those Eris brutes are chasing after me!

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: May Aqua's blessing be upon you during your journey!

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: An evil spirit is following you! Convert now or you'll die in a week!

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: Mitsurugi sure is handsome. Do you think he'd like to take care of me?

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: Those Eris followers are so close-minded! I feel like eating all of their bread!

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: Be careful when eating jelly slimes. The wrong technique could cost you your life.

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: Both the Order of Axis and myself welcome any and all donations!

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: Do you think Axel Hearts will help me recruit people into the Order of Axis?

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: That little beastman girl that sells vegetables in Axel is such a cutie.

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: These trials are a way to build the virtue I need to better spread my faith!

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: I know that the good Lady Aqua is watching over my efforts!

name: Game Title 1
quote_text: God's Blessing on this Wonderful World! Fantastic Days

name: Game Title 2
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Game Title 3
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: You want to celebrate my birthday? Then sign on the dotted line, and enter the wondrous Axis faith!

name: Arue 1 (Best Bod)
quote_text: The might of my clan pumps through my veins. Behold your doom, and despair!

name: Arue 2 (Best Bod)
quote_text: We're Magic Academy alumni. I suggest you stand down.

name: Arue 1 (Aspiring Author)
quote_text: I'm in the midst of penning my masterpiece...the Crimson Chronicles.

name: Arue 2 (Aspiring Author)
quote_text: Interesting... Conversations with you always seem to inspire me.

name: Arue 1 (Arch Wizard)
quote_text: Ohoho. Removing the seal over my eye would bring catastrophe upon the world.

name: Arue 2 (Arch Wizard)
quote_text: Would you like to see my hidden power?

name: Arue 1 (Stylish Debut)
quote_text: I am Arue, the soon-to-be famous author of the Crimson Chronicles!

name: Arue 2 (Stylish Debut)
quote_text: Funifura and Dodonko are classmates of mine from the Red Prison Magic Academy.

name: Arue 1 (Moonlit Meeting)
quote_text: I dwell in darkness; the moonlight shall never find me.

name: Arue 2 (Moonlit Meeting)
quote_text: I must do all my master says, no matter what? Amazing!

name: Arue 1 (Damsel in Distress)
quote_text: Flanked by vicious monsters on all sides. Someone—help!

name: Arue 2 (Damsel in Distress)
quote_text: Ugh. I allowed these mindless brutes to get the upper hand. Now look at me...

name: Arue 1 (Crimson Snow)
quote_text: What do you think of my snow Chomusuke?

name: Arue 2 (Crimson Snow)
quote_text: The snowman's missing something... How about a little blood?

name: Arue 1 (Hot Spring Cleansing)
quote_text: I get my best ideas when soaking in a good hot spring.

name: Arue 2 (Hot Spring Cleansing)
quote_text: I wonder if Megumin could dig us a hot spring with her explosion magic...

name: Arue 1 (Midnight Match)
quote_text: Let's get this pajama party going!

name: Arue 2 (Midnight Match)
quote_text: I couldn't sleep. Would you care to chat with me?

name: Arue 1 (Crimson Sunset)
quote_text: The sun setting over the sea is gorgeous. The eyes of Crimson Demons shine even redder in its light.

name: Arue 2 (Crimson Sunset)
quote_text: I hear the sound of crashing waves... It seems the ocean is passionate today.

name: Arue (Homeward Trek) 1
quote_text: Going on a quest with Megumin and Yunyun reminds me of our Academy days.

name: Arue (Homeward Trek) 2
quote_text: Megumin and Komekko are really close. Seeing them together always brings a smile to my face.

name: Arue (Secret Santa) 1
quote_text: Enshrouded in crimson attire, I bestow this gift upon you. It is yours to accept!

name: Arue (Secret Santa) 2
quote_text: This outfit and its color scheme are perfect for us Crimson Demons. Maybe it could be our official uniforms?

name: Arue 1 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: More stylish, more intelligent! My very existence will be a magnificent story...!

name: Arue 2 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: I am the legendary writer. You should take good care of my autograph.

name: Arue 1 (Your Wish)
quote_text: You've come a long way! Now, go ahead and order what you want....

name: Arue 2 (Your Wish)
quote_text: Ah, was serving customers this hard....

name: Arue 1 (Welcome to the Party)
quote_text: Trick of treat. Now, let us begin the party of darkness.

name: Arue 2 (Welcome to the Party)
quote_text: Disguising as a monster is new and fun.

name: Arue 1 (The Finest Figure)
quote_text: If you help me, I will make you wish come true.

name: Arue 2 (The Finest Figure)
quote_text: I think Dodonko's body is mature because she sleeps so much.

name: Arue (Endless Writing) 1
quote_text: A novel is a testament to an author, carved out after countless mistakes and wanderings.

name: Arue (Endless Writing) 2
quote_text: The more I write, the more lost I get in the labyrinth of questions and answers... Writing is an agonizing adventure.

name: Arue (Crimson Christmas) 1
quote_text: Everyone wearing red, including the one called Santa, is great.

name: Arue (Crimson Christmas) 2
quote_text: On a snowy night. An old man wearing clear red slowly approached me... Let's use this as the introduction for the new novel.

name: Arue 1 (Crimson Demon)
quote_text: I published an article about my village titled "Eternal Guide." Do give it a look.

name: Arue 2 (Crimson Demon)
quote_text: I think the path of the pen suits me far better.

name: Arue 1 (Beginner)
quote_text: I trust you read my letter?

name: Arue 2 (Beginner)
quote_text: The village has been as quiet as the grave since Megumin and Yunyun left.

name: Arue 1 (Dramatic Author)
quote_text: "You dare to oppose such a hero?! You shall taste my lightning!"

name: Arue 2 (Dramatic Author)
quote_text: Acting experience is great inspiration for my writing.

name: Arue 3 (Dramatic Author)
quote_text: Time to raise the curtain.

name: Arue 4 (Dramatic Author)
quote_text: The show must go on!

name: Arue 5 (Dramatic Author)
quote_text: Should I alter these costumes?

name: Arue 3 (Moonlit Meeting)
quote_text: I am the kunoichi who rules the night!

name: Arue 4 (Moonlit Meeting)
quote_text: This is the perfect attire for a Crimson Demon.

name: Arue 5 (Moonlit Meeting)
quote_text: Have you been charmed by my kunoichi technique?

name: Arue 6 (Moonlit Meeting)
quote_text: My kunai can pierce the smallest openings!

name: Arue 3 (Crimson Snow)
quote_text: Time to find the New Year's bargains!

name: Arue 4 (Crimson Snow)
quote_text: I'll be plenty warm wearing this.

name: Arue 5 (Crimson Snow)
quote_text: Snowy days are perfect for novel writing!

name: Arue 6 (Crimson Snow)
quote_text: Behold the spoils of war!

name: Battle 39
quote_text: Shining Eruption!

name: Battle 40
quote_text: You shall be engulfed in hellfire!

name: Arue 3 (Crimson Sunset)
quote_text: We're in for another hot summer.

name: Arue 4 (Crimson Sunset)
quote_text: The only problem with the sea is how defenseless it leaves us.

name: Arue 5 (Crimson Sunset)
quote_text: Oh... Sorry, can't talk now... Snow cones!

name: Arue 6 (Crimson Sunset)
quote_text: I think I like writing by the beach.

name: Battle 41
quote_text: I must unleash this forbidden power!

name: Battle 42
quote_text: Let the blood rage course through me!

name: Battle 43
quote_text: My crimson eye aches!

name: Arue (Secret Santa) 3
quote_text: This mad celebration of crimson has begun...

name: Arue (Secret Santa) 4
quote_text: Planning is the key to any successful event.

name: Arue (Secret Santa) 5
quote_text: Rejoice, on this holy night of chaos!

name: Arue (Secret Santa) 6
quote_text: I refuse to allow this night to end just yet!

name: Arue 3 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: My name is Arue! The living legend!

name: Arue 4 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: This is a prologue of a new story…!

name: Arue 5 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Let's write it down before I forget it.

name: Arue 6 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Put my soul into each stroke!

name: Arue 3 (Welcome to the Party)
quote_text: The festival of harvest begins…!

name: Arue 4 (Welcome to the Party)
quote_text: Do you like pranks?

name: Arue 5 (Welcome to the Party)
quote_text: Heeehee, sweets.

name: Arue 6 (Welcome to the Party)
quote_text: Let the party continue!

name: Arue (Endless Writing) 3
quote_text: Now, it's time to write.

name: Arue (Endless Writing) 4
quote_text: This is the start of a new story.

name: Arue (Endless Writing) 5
quote_text: The next protagonist... is you!

name: Arue (Endless Writing) 6
quote_text: I will end this paragraph.

name: Arue 6 (Dramatic Author)
quote_text: Heroic tales are my specialty.

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: I am Arue, most buxom of the Crimson Demons...and an aspiring author!

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: Those who disturb my reading will pay with their lives.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: I intend to be the first Crimson Demon to publish a bestseller.

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: This is no eyepatch. This magical seal restrains my demonic eye's rage.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: A Crimson Demon lives to master the art of...looking cool.

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: Unlike Yunyun and Megumin, I actually have some common sense.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: Behold this full-figured physique...and fear the awesome power it commands!

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: Once I've written my novel, would you like to be the first to read it?

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: Care to quest together? I'm sure we'd have a blast.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: Perhaps I'll write an adventure piece...one starring you.

name: Greeting
quote_text: Would you like a glimpse into the abyss?

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: No turning back now...

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: One step closer to greatness.

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: The time of awakening is upon us.

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: M-My magic powers...I'm losing control!

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: O magic power might...inhabit my blood, my body, and give me strength!

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: Is this what the world is yearning for?

name: Battle 1
quote_text: I suppose I don't mind pitching in.

name: Battle 2
quote_text: Blackest of black, and darkest of dark...I command thee to serve.

name: Battle 3
quote_text: I hear the wind weeping.

name: Battle 4
quote_text: Alas, I couldn't suppress my awesome power.

name: Battle 5
quote_text: Alas, today is no day for rejoicing.

name: Battle 6
quote_text: I hear the somber dirge of destruction.

name: Battle 7
quote_text: Feel my awesome power!

name: Battle 8
quote_text: Haaahh!

name: Battle 9
quote_text: My might is beastly. And you will feed my might!

name: Battle 10
quote_text: Sleep for all eternity!

name: Battle 11
quote_text: You've forced my hand.

name: Battle 12
quote_text: Light of the heavens, cleanse this unclean horde.

name: Battle 13
quote_text: Style is what really wins fights.

name: Battle 14
quote_text: Focus, Arue... Focus.

name: Battle 15
quote_text: Me? Lose? Unthinkable...

name: Battle 16
quote_text: The time has come!

name: Battle 17
quote_text: I let my guard down... How foolish.

name: Battle 18
quote_text: In time, our victory will present itself.

name: Battle 19
quote_text: There's no getting around this.

name: Battle 20
quote_text: My power shall be etched upon your memory!

name: Battle 21
quote_text: This will make great material for my next novel.

name: Battle 22
quote_text: My heroic tale continues!

name: Battle 23
quote_text: Now this will be a sight to behold!

name: Battle 24
quote_text: My spirit shall never waver!

name: Battle 25
quote_text: Such a fleeting life...

name: Battle 26
quote_text: My pen yearns for the page!

name: Battle 27
quote_text: Behold the power of darkness!

name: Battle 28
quote_text: Feel my power!

name: Battle 29
quote_text: Your story ends here!

name: Battle 30
quote_text: The ideas simply keep coming!

name: Battle 31
quote_text: Surrender your entire self to me.

name: Battle 32
quote_text: Cursed Lightning!

name: Battle 33
quote_text: Aaahhh!

name: Battle 34
quote_text: My strength wanes...

name: Battle 35
quote_text: Pay close attention to what's about to happen.

name: Battle 36
quote_text: Are you saying this is to be my fate?!

name: Battle 37
quote_text: This defies all reason!

name: Battle 38
quote_text: This is my destiny!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: I dare say you're nicer than you let on.

name: Misc 2
quote_text: I never dreamed I'd make friends outside the village.

name: Misc 3
quote_text: I'd think twice before angering a Crimson Demon.

name: Misc 4
quote_text: Time to seek out inspiration for my novel!

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Megumin's eyepatch was a present from me.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: What should I write to Yunyun about next, I wonder?

name: Misc 7
quote_text: Delight me with stories of your adventures. They might spark my writer's inspiration.

name: Misc 8
quote_text: I have a plot in mind for my story. Could you act out this script for me?

name: Misc 9
quote_text: Would Yunyun be surprised that I wrote the romance novel she's reading?

name: Misc 10
quote_text: Victory has no meaning for Crimson Demons unless you look cool earning it.

name: Misc 11
quote_text: Detonate! Sorry, I just wanted to try saying that.

name: Misc 12
quote_text: Mia and Amy's ears are fascinating. I'd like to sit back and just watch them.

name: Misc 13
quote_text: Would you consider being a character model for my new book?

name: Misc 14
quote_text: They say humans have eyes facing front to keep them moving forward.

name: Misc 15
quote_text: It's awfully windy today.

name: Misc 16
quote_text: Rrgh... The power behind my left eye is going berserk!

name: Misc 17
quote_text: Hmph! I smell a new plot point!

name: Misc 18
quote_text: My name is Arue! Now introduce yourself, and make it good.

name: Misc 19
quote_text: What do you think of my eyepatch? Stylish, no?

name: Misc 20
quote_text: I'm thinking of doing a story about dancers.

name: Misc 21
quote_text: If you want to be in the Crimson Chronicles, show me your stuff.

name: Misc 22
quote_text: My left eye aches... The awakening draws near.

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: A Crimson Demon-style introduction will earn you friends for sure.

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: I'd like you to be the model for the total loser in my next story.

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: Do you want my eyepatch? It's yours. I have plenty of extras.

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: I want to be a popular author.

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: A story based on Megumin and Komekko might be interesting.

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: I never tire of watching Yunyun. However, that doesn't mean I want to base a novel on her.

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: If you're in search of a cool nickname, you've come to the right place.

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: In order to write a good novel, you need to experience life to its fullest.

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: Can I talk to you for a bit? I need to take a break from writing.

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: Now is not the time for me to unleash my true power. However, that day will come.

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: Oh...! Be still, my evil kin who dwells behind my eyepatch!

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: Perhaps "Warrior Wordsmith" would be a good pen name for me from now on?

name: Game Title 1
quote_text: God's Blessing on this Wonderful World! Fantastic Days

name: Game Title 2
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Game Title 3
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: My, you remembered. You're too kind. This will be a birthday I won't soon forget.

name: Mitsurugi 1 (The Chosen One)
quote_text: Any foe who stands in my way will taste this mystic blade!

name: Mitsurugi 2 (The Chosen One)
quote_text: Stand back. I cannot allow a lady, not even an adventurer, to risk mortal danger.

name: Mitsurugi 1 (Follower of the Goddess)
quote_text: G-Goddess Aqua, it is I, your loyal servant, Kyouya Mitsurugi! Who is this scruffy-looking man you are with?

name: Mitsurugi 2 (Follower of the Goddess)
quote_text: Kazuma Satou, you conniving rogue! You truly are the lowest of the low!

name: Mitsurugi 1 (Sword Master)
quote_text: Do not underestimate the power of a battle-tested sword master.

name: Mitsurugi 2 (Sword Master)
quote_text: Gram is a cursed sword, bestowed upon me by the goddess. Pawning it is unthinkable!

name: Mitsurugi 1 (Casual)
quote_text: Holidays are far and few between. Perhaps a little relaxation is in order.

name: Mitsurugi 2 (Casual)
quote_text: I hone my body as a tool to mete out justice.

name: Mitsurugi 1 (Beginner)
quote_text: If I am to one day defeat the Devil King, daily training is imperative.

name: Mitsurugi 2 (Beginner)
quote_text: Kyouya Mitsurugi's my name. Kyouya, Mitsurugi...use whichever you prefer.

name: Mitsurugi 1 (Dreamy Dealer)
quote_text: There's no need for Lady Luck with me on your side.

name: Mitsurugi 2 (Dreamy Dealer)
quote_text: If I win at roulette, join me on my journey to defeat the Devil King.

name: Mitsurugi 1 (Heroic Grace)
quote_text: It's an honor to accompany you, Lady Iris. Please, take my hand.

name: Mitsurugi 2 (Heroic Grace)
quote_text: Thank you for the invitation to the ball. Allow me to be your dance partner.

name: Mitsurugi 1 (Twilight Ninja)
quote_text: If you want to be a ninja, watch and learn.

name: Mitsurugi 2 (Twilight Ninja)
quote_text: Ninjas are part of my culture. I can learn from their strength.

name: Mitsurugi 1 (A Hero's Treasure)
quote_text: Thank you, my goddess, I shall treasure your blessing forever!

name: Mitsurugi 2 (A Hero's Treasure)
quote_text: I would walk through fire for Lady Aqua!

name: Mitsurugi 1 (Personal Bodyguard)
quote_text: You think you can defeat a sword master with snowballs? How ridi—Mmphh!

name: Mitsurugi 2 (Personal Bodyguard)
quote_text: Curse you, Kazuma Satou! How dare you throw snowballs at Lady Aqua!

name: Mitsurugi 1 (Familiar Pattern)
quote_text: This is the end for you! Wait, what the—? What happened to Gram?

name: Mitsurugi 2 (Familiar Pattern)
quote_text: Kazuma Satooooou!!! Why must you do this?!

name: Mitsurugi 1 (Luxurious Hero)
quote_text: I feel like the prince of a distant land. So, does this outfit suit me?

name: Mitsurugi 2 (Luxurious Hero)
quote_text: I'm wearing this outfit due to the heat. Lady Aqua wants some fruit that only grows in warm climates.

name: Mitsurugi 1 (Splashing Swimmer)
quote_text: I'm a pretty good swimmer. Rest easy, and leave the ocean quests to me!

name: Mitsurugi 2 (Splashing Swimmer)
quote_text: Lady Aqua looks so majestic in the water... I can't believe she catches fish with her bare hands!

name: Mitsurugi (Dedicated Disciple) 1
quote_text: I'm sure it can't hurt to learn martial arts. I can't always rely on my beloved sword, Gram!

name: Mitsurugi (Dedicated Disciple) 2
quote_text: Easy to move in, and a dapper design. Lady Aqua's talent knowns no bounds!

name: Mitsurugi (Hopeless Proposal) 1
quote_text: Kazuma Satou is upstaging me?! Not if I have something to say about it!

name: Mitsurugi (Hopeless Proposal) 2
quote_text: He'd do well to remember I am Mitsurugi, wielder of the cursed sword!

name: Mitsurugi (Supportive Kindness) 1
quote_text: This is a little embarrassing, but take a look at my outfit. It's from back home.

name: Mitsurugi (Supportive Kindness) 2
quote_text: What do you mean I don't look the part? A true hero can fight regardless of their attire.

name: Mitsurugi 1 (Hero's Adventure)
quote_text: Let's go. It's fine, the hero Mitsurugi is with you.

name: Mitsurugi 2 (Hero's Adventure)
quote_text: Something wrong? You can tell me anything.

name: Mitsurugi (Legendary Adventurer) 1
quote_text: I will win this fight no matter what. The legend starts here!

name: Mitsurugi (Legendary Adventurer) 2
quote_text: It's fine, I will protect you even if it costs me my life.

name: Mitsurugi 3 (Dreamy Dealer)
quote_text: Let the game begin!

name: Mitsurugi 4 (Dreamy Dealer)
quote_text: I'll be earning some chips.

name: Mitsurugi 5 (Dreamy Dealer)
quote_text: Gamble in moderation.

name: Mitsurugi 3 (Twilight Ninja)
quote_text: Ninja Mitsurugi is ready for battle!

name: Mitsurugi 4 (Twilight Ninja)
quote_text: My ninjutsu is at your service.

name: Mitsurugi 5 (Twilight Ninja)
quote_text: I'll cut down anyone who deserves it.

name: Mitsurugi 6 (Twilight Ninja)
quote_text: Ninja is an impressive job class.
