quote_text: How do these clothes look?

name: Mitsurugi 4 (Personal Bodyguard)
quote_text: The cold doesn't affect me!

name: Mitsurugi 5 (Personal Bodyguard)
quote_text: Want to go on a trip with me?

name: Mitsurugi 6 (Personal Bodyguard)
quote_text: I'll buy you something to keep warm.

name: Battle 39
quote_text: Rune of Saber!

name: Battle 40
quote_text: My cursed sword cuts deep!

name: Mitsurugi 3 (Luxurious Hero)
quote_text: Do you want to go on a trip with me?

name: Mitsurugi 4 (Luxurious Hero)
quote_text: It's all going according to my plan.

name: Mitsurugi 5 (Luxurious Hero)
quote_text: I think this flower suits you perfectly.

name: Mitsurugi 6 (Luxurious Hero)
quote_text: I'll wear whatever clothes you want me to!

name: Battle 41
quote_text: I'm on it!

name: Battle 42
quote_text: Count on me.

name: Battle 43
quote_text: I can continue the fight!

name: Mitsurugi (Dedicated Disciple) 3
quote_text: With the power of a dragon!

name: Mitsurugi (Dedicated Disciple) 4
quote_text: And the nimbleness of a beast!

name: Mitsurugi (Dedicated Disciple) 5
quote_text: We should close the event with a show of gratitude.

name: Mitsurugi (Dedicated Disciple) 6
quote_text: Behold the power of my martial arts!

name: Mitsurugi (Supportive Kindness) 3
quote_text: Do you want to meet the real me?

name: Mitsurugi (Supportive Kindness) 4
quote_text: Observe! True power and style.

name: Mitsurugi (Supportive Kindness) 5
quote_text: A warrior must also look good.

name: Mitsurugi (Supportive Kindness) 6
quote_text: How do I look, my goddess?!

name: Mitsurugi 3 (Hero's Adventure)
quote_text: You can rely on me.

name: Mitsurugi 4 (Hero's Adventure)
quote_text: Leave it to me!

name: Mitsurugi 5 (Hero's Adventure)
quote_text: Are you hurt?

name: Mitsurugi 6 (Hero's Adventure)
quote_text: You can rest if you're tired.

name: Mitsurugi (Legendary Adventurer) 3
quote_text: Did you think you could win against the legendary hero?

name: Mitsurugi (Legendary Adventurer) 4
quote_text: This power... I don't think I'm going to lose.

name: Mitsurugi (Legendary Adventurer) 5
quote_text: This victory was decided from the start.

name: Mitsurugi (Legendary Adventurer) 6
quote_text: There is nothing else to mention about that.

name: Mitsurugi 6 (Dreamy Dealer)
quote_text: Should I leave a tip?

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: Kyouya Mitsurugi's my name! For the love of the goddess, do try to remember that.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: I trust you're serious about facing the Devil King?

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: Kazuma Satou, your brazen insults to the goddess Aqua shall not go unpunished!

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: They call me the Man of the Mystic Blade. But I assure you...I'm just one of the boys.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: You'll be a corpse by sundown with that gear. I offer you the tools of a real knight.

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: Only I can wield the cursed sword Gram. It would be useless to you.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: Someday, I'll become a hero worthy of the goddess's praise!

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: The next quest calls! Fear not, I will protect you.

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: Not even an ancient dragon stands a chance before the ultimate sword master!

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: If you wish to taste the sweetest of victories, do not stray from my side!

name: Greeting
quote_text: The Devil King will fall by my hand!

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: I am protected by the goddess, it seems.

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: Yet again, I have attained new heights of strength. All the more reason for you to follow me.

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: On Aqua's name, I swear to become stronger!

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: Heh, a real hero never ceases his advance.

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: Behold the power of a hero chosen by the goddess herself!

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: The Devil King shall fall by my hand!

name: Battle 1
quote_text: A true hero always prevails!

name: Battle 2
quote_text: Prepare to witness the skills of a true knight!

name: Battle 3
quote_text: Such is the might of the Chosen One.

name: Battle 4
quote_text: I dedicate this victory to the goddess!

name: Battle 5
quote_text: Something's not quite right...

name: Battle 6
quote_text: A hero like me...vanquished? But how...

name: Battle 7
quote_text: Behold the might of a hero!

name: Battle 8
quote_text: Haaah!

name: Battle 9
quote_text: Victory is mine!

name: Battle 10
quote_text: Begone!

name: Battle 11
quote_text: Give me strength, O mystic blade!

name: Battle 12
quote_text: Protecting one's allies is the mark of a true hero.

name: Battle 13
quote_text: I will save this world! I have sworn before the goddess!

name: Battle 14
quote_text: Nrrgh.

name: Battle 15
quote_text: Oh, my goddess...

name: Battle 16
quote_text: The next blow will settle this!

name: Battle 17
quote_text: This rabble doesn't know when to quit!

name: Battle 18
quote_text: I'm always here for you.

name: Battle 19
quote_text: I'll take it from here!

name: Battle 20
quote_text: I am Kyouya Mitsurugi!

name: Battle 21
quote_text: I was chosen by the goddess herself!

name: Battle 22
quote_text: Defeat the Devil King!

name: Battle 23
quote_text: I shall be the one to save this world!

name: Battle 24
quote_text: I can't let the goddess see me like this...

name: Battle 25
quote_text: I will not let it end like this!

name: Battle 26
quote_text: I will show no mercy.

name: Battle 27
quote_text: I shall be the victor here!

name: Battle 28
quote_text: Allow me to handle this!

name: Battle 29
quote_text: Just accept your defeat with grace!

name: Battle 30
quote_text: Are you all right?

name: Battle 31
quote_text: I can't lose until I've saved the world!

name: Battle 32
quote_text: This is the blade of the chosen one!

name: Battle 33
quote_text: Yaaaaaagh!

name: Battle 34
quote_text: Is this how it ends...?

name: Battle 35
quote_text: I feel a surge of strength!

name: Battle 36
quote_text: I'm not finished yet!

name: Battle 37
quote_text: I won't let you forget me!

name: Battle 38
quote_text: I'm here now!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: I sense you are a person of character.

name: Misc 2
quote_text: There's a spot for you in my party, if you like.

name: Misc 3
quote_text: I am Mitsurugi, Man of the Mystic Blade!

name: Misc 4
quote_text: You were wise to choose me for your party.

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Kazuma Satou's party is no place for a goddess like Aqua!

name: Misc 6
quote_text: The happiness of the people is my own. That is why I walk the path of the hero.

name: Misc 7
quote_text: If I see someone in need, I help them. Such is the duty of one who claims to be a hero.

name: Misc 8
quote_text: Want to join my party? Let's defeat the Devil King together.

name: Misc 9
quote_text: Lady Aqua takes my breath away every time I see her.

name: Misc 10
quote_text: Melissa randomly asks me out on quests lately. Why is that?

name: Misc 11
quote_text: Even I take a day off to relax every once in a while.

name: Misc 12
quote_text: My interest in romance? Saving the world is my priority now.

name: Misc 13
quote_text: Kazuma Satou is telling Princess Iris strange rumors about me!

name: Misc 14
quote_text: It is best to act in a way that does not bother the ladies.

name: Misc 15
quote_text: My sword Gram is proof of my connection to Lady Aqua.

name: Misc 16
quote_text: One day, I will free Lady Aqua from the claws of Kazuma Satou!

name: Misc 17
quote_text: Only I can wield Gram. Holding it would mean nothing for you.

name: Misc 18
quote_text: If you are in trouble, you can call on me without hesitation.

name: Misc 19
quote_text: I want to help those in distress. That's what a true hero does.

name: Misc 20
quote_text: The women around Kazuma Satou all seem to treat me coldly.

name: Misc 21
quote_text: I'll beat you the next time we meet! I will spare no effort!

name: Misc 22
quote_text: I, and no one else, will be the one to slay the Devil King!

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: To me, the smiles of those I've saved are the best reward.

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: I have to keep leveling up if I'm to defeat the Devil King.

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: With today's quest, I shall strive to fulfill the duty Lady Aqua gave me.

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: Kazuma Satou beat me even though he's lower-level. I must train harder.

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: I love children. Seeing Mia warms my heart.

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: Everyone gets my name wrong... It isn't that hard to remember, is it?

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: The Crimson Demons are quite powerful. I wish I had one in my party...

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: Have you seen Axel Hearts perform? They put on an amazing show!

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: You want to train with me? Very well, let's push ourselves to new limits!

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: The Devil King continues to bring suffering upon the people. He will pay for his villainy!

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: Is this...the power of a hero that resides within me?

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: As a defender of the people and wielder of a cursed sword, I must always strive to improve myself.

name: Game Title 1
quote_text: God's Blessing on this Wonderful World! Fantastic Days

name: Game Title 2
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Game Title 3
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: Thank you for remembering my birthday. I don't need anything expensive.

name: Dust 1 (Delinquent Adventurer)
quote_text: Not even a greeting, eh? I'm not okay with that.

name: Dust 2 (Delinquent Adventurer)
quote_text: I thought any quest'd be a breeze for a party chock full of advanced job classes... That was before.

name: Dust 1 (Succubus Shop Regular)
quote_text: Oh ho ho. Man, do I loooooove this shop!

name: Dust 2 (Succubus Shop Regular)
quote_text: All the town's male adventurers visit this place on the regular.

name: Dust 1 (Warrior)
quote_text: Hey, watch your mouth. No hoodlum fights like this!

name: Dust 2 (Warrior)
quote_text: I'm not a questing man. That said, I do have loads of debt to pay off.

name: Dust 1 (Casual)
quote_text: I could use a drink. Or ten.

name: Dust 2 (Casual)
quote_text: The cold doesn't bug me, even like this. It's my current financial state that chills me to the bone...

name: Dust 1 (Beginner)
quote_text: Everyone in town knows who I am.

name: Dust 2 (Beginner)
quote_text: New adventurers gotta buy me one drink each. It's an Axel tradition!

name: Dust 1 (Begging Forgiveness)
quote_text: Hey, I'm on my knees here! Please, just think of it as helping Rin!

name: Dust 2 (Begging Forgiveness)
quote_text: I know this is a lot to ask, but you're the only ones I can turn to!

name: Dust 1 (My Treasure)
quote_text: If this magic lamp is real, I'll have all the money and women I want!

name: Dust 2 (My Treasure)
quote_text: I was the first one to discover the lamp, so call me "master"!

name: Dust 1 (A Man's Duty)
quote_text: No one will lay a finger on this town or its people!

name: Dust 2 (A Man's Duty)
quote_text: You don't need an excuse to help people...right, Brother?

name: Dust 1 (Hot Spring Thrills)
quote_text: There is one thing a man must always do at a hot spring!

name: Dust 2 (Hot Spring Thrills)
quote_text: Is Yunyun really the same age as Megumin?

name: Dust 1 (School Bully)
quote_text: As long as I draw breath, nobody will run this town except me. Got it?

name: Dust 2 (School Bully)
quote_text: This uniform has too many buttons! What a pain... Well, maybe I just won't fasten them.

name: Dust 1 (High Roller)
quote_text: The tide's about to turn my way! I'll bet my clothes if I have to—I'm all-in!

name: Dust 2 (High Roller)
quote_text: My name's Dust... I'm the greatest gambler that ever lived!

name: Dust 1 (Monster Bait)
quote_text: I'm begging you, untie me already! I'd rather not be lunch for some hungry orc!

name: Dust 2 (Monster Bait)
quote_text: Ugh... That was a close one! Good thing you came by when you did!

name: Dust (Chronic Oversleeper) 1
quote_text: What's all the racket? It's too early for this. Wait, did we have a quest today?

name: Dust (Chronic Oversleeper) 2
quote_text: You know when you want to sleep but can't? Like when I make a reservation at you-know-where.

name: Dust (Pro Procrastinator) 1
quote_text: Take orders without without getting tips, you gotta be kidding!

name: Dust (Pro Procrastinator) 2
quote_text: Are there any beautiful helpers out there willing to give me money…

name: Dust 1 (Unexpected Confession)
quote_text: Kazuma can be quite reliable, he can be pretty smart sometimes.

name: Dust 2 (Unexpected Confession)
quote_text: I'm the closest guy to Kazuma. We share tons of secrets.

name: Dust 1 (Delinquent Guard)
quote_text: It's important to prevent accidents from happening. I'm gonna make no one complain. Hehehe….

name: Dust 2 (Delinquent Guard)
quote_text: What's wrong with staring? I'm a look out, it's my job!

name: Dust 1 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Don’t think I’m my usual self! Watch out for the legendary adventurer, Dust!

name: Dust 2 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Now, no one can call me a thug anymore. I will beat them all with this power, and... Hahaha.

name: Dust (In Sync) 1
quote_text: Hehe, I won't go easy on you.

name: Dust (In Sync) 2
quote_text: Brother's plan is as incredible as I expected... Oh, it's nothing!

name: Dust 1 (Super Sledder)
quote_text: Hey, beautiful. Wanna sled with the top sledder?

name: Dust 2 (Super Sledder)
quote_text: Oh yeah! I'm the king o' the hill, or rather, the mountain!

name: Dust 3 (Super Sledder)
quote_text: You messed with the wrong man!

name: Dust 4 (Super Sledder)
quote_text: Nice, this'll warm me right up.

name: Dust 5 (Super Sledder)
quote_text: C'mon, gang! Let's get sleddin'!

name: Dust 6 (Super Sledder)
quote_text: There's no low I won't stoop to! Hehehe.

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: I can team up with you, sure. Just don't hold me back.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: Ask me anything about Axel. I know this town like the back of my hand.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: Lend me some coin? Pretty please? I'll give it back, I promise!

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: *Sigh* I wish coins would just rain from the sky once in awhile.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: Oh, yeah! The drinks taste better when someone else is buying!

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: Seriously. Is it too much to ask for a smoking hot babe who'll spoil me blind?

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: Questing, are we? Fine, but keep it to something easy, would ya?

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: Hey, you're looking glum. Let's hit up the tavern! You're buying.

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: I think I'll stop by my favorite shop tonight, hehe.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: You're my best pal, y'know that? So...lend me some money?

name: Greeting
quote_text: You want my help? Hook me up with a lovely lady and we'll see.

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: I'm not big on hard work, but I could stand to get a tad stronger.

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: I'm gonna smoke ya good!

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: Oh yeah! Jackpot, baby!

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: You can work for me any time. As my lackey.

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: Gotta try once in a while.

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: Hwahaha! Oh man, I can't stop laughing!

name: Battle 1
quote_text: Do your worst, ya bum!

name: Battle 2
quote_text: I better not break a sweat.

name: Battle 3
quote_text: Wimps can get stuffed.

name: Battle 4
quote_text: I know I'm gorgeous, but don't fall for me.

name: Battle 5
quote_text: I'll...let you off the hook for today.

name: Battle 6
quote_text: L-let me go. It's them you want...

name: Battle 7
quote_text: Try this on for size!

name: Battle 8
quote_text: Eat this!

name: Battle 9
quote_text: You're outta luck now, bud!

name: Battle 10
quote_text: You're gonna regret that!

name: Battle 11
quote_text: I got this, easy-peasy.

name: Battle 12
quote_text: They won't know what hit 'em.

name: Battle 13
quote_text: Someone owes me a drink when all this is over!

name: Battle 14
quote_text: Rrrgh!

name: Battle 15
quote_text: This just isn't my day...

name: Battle 16
quote_text: I'll do some real damage.

name: Battle 17
quote_text: Eesh. Can I leave now?

name: Battle 18
quote_text: Okay, give 'em hell. I'm just here for moral support.

name: Battle 19
quote_text: I'm gonna rip you a new one!

name: Battle 20
quote_text: I heard there was a real looker here.

name: Battle 21
quote_text: I've come this far! No point backing down now!

name: Battle 22
quote_text: Let's celebrate our victory!

name: Battle 23
quote_text: Let's live it up tonight!

name: Battle 24
quote_text: Forget about today, okay?

name: Battle 25
quote_text: This is why I don't like taking on quests.

name: Battle 26
quote_text: Take this!

name: Dust 3 (Hot Spring Thrills)
quote_text: Let's work up a sweat before our bath!

name: Dust 4 (Hot Spring Thrills)
quote_text: Just calm down and let us in.

name: Dust 5 (Hot Spring Thrills)
quote_text: All right, time for an eyeful!

name: Dust 6 (Hot Spring Thrills)
quote_text: Now, where's the women's bath?

name: Battle 39
quote_text: Brace for my best!

name: Battle 40
quote_text: Step back or you're gonna get hurt!

name: Dust 3 (School Bully)
quote_text: Hey! Put your back into it!

name: Dust 4 (School Bully)
quote_text: I'll show you who's boss!

name: Dust 5 (School Bully)
quote_text: I ain't even breaking a sweat!

name: Dust 6 (School Bully)
quote_text: Would you like to take my second button?

name: Battle 41
quote_text: See how you like this!

name: Battle 42
quote_text: This is gonna cost ya!

name: Battle 43
quote_text: Let's do this!

name: Dust (Chronic Oversleeper) 3
quote_text: Buzz off, I'm tired!

name: Dust (Chronic Oversleeper) 4
quote_text: No one likes a cold stomach, am I right!

name: Dust (Chronic Oversleeper) 5
quote_text: I'm done for the day! It's bedtime!

name: Dust (Chronic Oversleeper) 6
quote_text: I won't sacrifice my beauty sleep for this!

name: Dust (Pro Procrastinator) 3
quote_text: Ah~ I would've love to take a day off work if I could…

name: Dust (Pro Procrastinator) 4
quote_text: You don't need to help, Rin!

name: Dust (Pro Procrastinator) 5
quote_text: I should take a rest now that I'm done.

name: Dust (Pro Procrastinator) 6
quote_text: I didn't have to help.

name: Dust 3 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Feel every ounce of my power!

name: Dust 4 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Don’t think I’m my usual self!

name: Dust 5 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: You’re so weak that it makes me yawn.

name: Dust 6 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: This gear… I like it!

name: Battle 27
quote_text: Well, if I must!

name: Battle 28
quote_text: You really think you can beat me?

name: Battle 29
quote_text: This is a piece of cake!

name: Battle 30
quote_text: You had to stick your nose where it didn't belong.

name: Battle 31
quote_text: I've gotta show off every once in a while.

name: Battle 32
quote_text: If you're gonna do it, do it right!

name: Battle 33
quote_text: Whoa!

name: Battle 34
quote_text: I-I think I'm gonna head back early.

name: Battle 35
quote_text: I'm feelin' good about this!

name: Battle 36
quote_text: Someone, help me!

name: Battle 37
quote_text: What dream should I choose?

name: Battle 38
quote_text: I always come through when it counts!

name: Dust 3 (My Treasure)
quote_text: I am here to find that lamp!

name: Dust 4 (My Treasure)
quote_text: A man lives for his desires!

name: Dust 5 (My Treasure)
quote_text: The wish I want from the lamp...

name: Dust 6 (My Treasure)
quote_text: I want to have as much fun in life as possible!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: I'll take you to a shop that'll blow your socks off!

name: Misc 2
quote_text: Anytime you need a hand, just holler.

name: Misc 3
quote_text: I'll show you how we do things in Axel!

name: Misc 4
quote_text: Need my help? You better have the coin, then!

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Kudos to Kazuma. He's doing a bang-up job with that party of his.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: Nobles and royalty... All a bunch o' snooty, stuck-up losers if you ask me.

name: Misc 7
quote_text: How much have I spent at my favorite shop, you ask? Couldn't say...I live in the now.

name: Misc 8
quote_text: Stop rambling and buy me a drink already!

name: Misc 9
quote_text: A quest? I'm exhausted, so no thanks!

name: Misc 10
quote_text: See that girl over there? Me-yow. Hehehe...

name: Misc 11
quote_text: Rin is always taking care of me. I gotta give her a break.

name: Misc 12
quote_text: I'm not afraid to put someone in their place when necessary.

name: Misc 13
quote_text: Yunyun is always alone. I should invite her on a quest.

name: Misc 14
quote_text: Hey, bro. Wanna go to that special shop? Eh? Ehhh?

name: Misc 15
quote_text: How much do I owe Rin now? I don't wanna think about it.

name: Misc 16
quote_text: Lend me some coin? I'll pay you back double. C'mon, I'm begging ya!

name: Misc 17
quote_text: Ah, I sure would like a pretty lady to pamper me.

name: Misc 18
quote_text: Let's go to Arcanretia. We can peek in on the girls!

name: Misc 19
quote_text: It's my birthday. Tomorrow is, too. So buy me a drink!

name: Misc 20
quote_text: I really can't stomach nobles. Well, besides Darkness and Cielo.

name: Misc 21
quote_text: May the gods grant me money, women, and power!

name: Misc 22
quote_text: Kazuma, we're like brothers. So buy me a drink, eh?

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: As one of Axel's leading adventurers, I have to teach the newbies respect.

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: How much debt do I have? Why should I tell you?!

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: If you buy me some bubbly, I'll gladly cast away my pride!

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: I don't want to quest with Melissa. She'll just steal my cut.

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: I don't think I'm nearly as bad as Kazuma. What do you think?

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: Taking regular breaks is important to one's well-being. C'mon, let's get some bubbly!

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: I ain't got any money, but seeing Amy at the veggie shop is free.

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: If you're ever in jail, let me know. I know exactly how to make the most of your stay.

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: Darkness and Cielo are exceptions, but nobles are rarely good people.

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: Have you heard of any quests that are super easy, high-paying, and impressive?

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: Heh! This'll have the girls swooning after yours truly.

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: I'll have this town eating out of the palm of my hand before long.

quote_text: God's Blessing on this Wonderful World! Fantastic Days

name: Game Title 2
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Game Title 3
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: It's my b-day, so let's party 'til we drop! Ha, just like every day for me!

name: Rin 1 (Certified Wizard)
quote_text: Hey, hands off my friends!

name: Rin 2 (Certified Wizard)
quote_text: I don't go down easy. That's a wizard's pride, you know?

name: Rin 1 (Single Lady)
quote_text: I don't believe it... I'm surrounded by morons!

name: Rin 2 (Single Lady)
quote_text: Dust is the literal worst...the crown king of boorish oafs.

name: Rin 1 (Wizard)
quote_text: There's only one way I do things...my way!

name: Rin 2 (Wizard)
quote_text: Going on a quest? I'd be happy to lend a hand.

name: Rin 1 (Casual)
quote_text: Hanging around town's a nice change of pace sometimes.

name: Rin 2 (Casual)
quote_text: I was never much for dresses and frills, this right here's my style.

name: Rin 1 (Beginner)
quote_text: Us adventurers have to stick together.

name: Rin 2 (Beginner)
quote_text: Beginner spells are actually pretty handy. I should learn a few someday...

name: Rin 1 (Winter Wonderland)
quote_text: If only my worries would disappear into the snow, like a clean, white slate.

name: Rin 2 (Winter Wonderland)
quote_text: I like snow. Sure, it's cold...but it's oh so beautiful, too.

name: Rin 3 (Winter Wonderland)
quote_text: Can't a girl be left alone with her thoughts?

name: Rin 4 (Winter Wonderland)
quote_text: Let's end this quickly! A blizzard's coming.

name: Rin 5 (Winter Wonderland)
quote_text: Want to make a snowman?

name: Rin 6 (Winter Wonderland)
quote_text: Snow sprites are adorable.

name: Rin 1 (Female Foe)
quote_text: You can't just go around stealing underwear like that! You'll be punished!

name: Rin 2 (Female Foe)
quote_text: Judging by his character, it's only natural to assume Dust did it.

name: Rin 1 (Sun-soaked)
quote_text: We came all this way to the beach, so we have to enjoy ourselves.

name: Rin 2 (Sun-soaked)
quote_text: This beach is the perfect place to burn off all the stress Dust causes me!

name: Rin 1 (Watch Your Step)
quote_text: Ouch... I couldn't attack even if I wanted to.

name: Rin 2 (Watch Your Step)
quote_text: Kazuma's tactics are impressive, but he should brief us first!

name: Rin 1 (Laundry Day)
quote_text: Housework may be tiring, but cleaning feels good.

name: Rin 2 (Laundry Day)
quote_text: It's hard to relax in a maid uniform... Why are the skirts so long?

name: Rin 1 (Fateful Throw)
quote_text: I absolutely hate losing... Everything is riding on this dice throw!

name: Rin 2 (Fateful Throw)
quote_text: It's Dust and his crew. Of course they're going to demand some strange punishment for the loser.

name: Rin 1 (Windstorm Kunoichi)
quote_text: Tornado ninja arts, huh? Can I just use wind magic instead?

name: Rin 2 (Windstorm Kunoichi)
quote_text: Ninjas are so cool. I hear they come from Kazuma's hometown. I'd like to meet one someday.

name: Rin 1 (Summer Sharpshooter)
quote_text: The shooting gallery is harder than I thought... I'm surprised Komekko is so good at it.

name: Rin 2 (Summer Sharpshooter)
quote_text: So people wear this sort of thing where Kazuma's from? It's very comfortable and cool.

name: Rin (Firepower is Key) 1
quote_text: Great fried rice is all about high heat. I'll use my magic to make it light, fluffy, and delicious!

name: Rin (Firepower is Key) 2
quote_text: This getup really accentuates my body shape.

name: Rin (Tender Feelings) 1
quote_text: If I give Dust chocolate, it'll go straight to his head. Oh well, I guess I can let it slide for today.

name: Rin (Tender Feelings) 2
quote_text: Making chocolates with friends is one of the best things about Valentine's Day.

name: Rin 1 (Class President)
quote_text: I am used to giving advices to others. Thanks to someone.

name: Rin 2 (Class President)
quote_text: I get more nervous when I wear neat clothes.

name: Rin 1 (Sunbathing)
quote_text: Ah… Taking a nap in the sun is so nice.

name: Rin 2 (Sunbathing)
quote_text: I suddenly feel like eating salt grilled saury… meow.

name: Rin 1 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: With this, I will be able to support Dust better... N-Never mind!

name: Rin 2 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Am I a legend…? I'll do my best, so it doesn't just seem that way!

name: Rin (Everyone, It's Dinner Time) 1
quote_text: Let's not cross lines just because the quest was a great success, everyone.

name: Rin (Everyone, It's Dinner Time) 2
quote_text: Hehe, despite everything, it's fun to be a part of a reliable party.

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: It's not easy when you're partners with the town hoodlum.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: H-hey, you! This tail's not for touching!

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: I haven't picked up any beginner spells yet.

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: Magic power is second nature to the Crimson Demons. I'm almost envious.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: Dust is a real deadbeat. Don't EVER lend him money, you hear me?

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: I'm getting peckish. Let's grab something to eat, yeah?

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: Kazuma's job class isn't anything to write home about, but he's sharp. Makes him a good leader.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: All I do is take care of others. Will I ever have time to do the same for myself?

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: Why oh why can I not leave that wreck of a man be?

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: You seem down. Be nice to yourself, okay?

name: Greeting
quote_text: I've got your intermediate magic needs covered.

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: Hey, I think I'm growing up quite nicely.

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: I'm not pulling my punches, just so you know.

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: My wizard's instinct tells me I'm stronger.

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: This is one move I'll bet you've never seen.

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: Dust would turn tail if he had to face me now.

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: I'll be a famous wizard before you know it!

name: Battle 1
quote_text: We can do anything as a team!

name: Battle 2
quote_text: You should know, that's the last time I save your butt.

name: Battle 3
quote_text: Chalk up one more win to teamwork!

name: Battle 4
quote_text: Let's celebrate at the tavern!

name: Battle 5
quote_text: Ugh... I really need to pick my battles.

name: Battle 6
quote_text: Uh oh. Clean out of magic power...

name: Battle 7
quote_text: Ugh, enough!

name: Battle 8
quote_text: Hyah!

name: Battle 9
quote_text: Ready to get mangled?

name: Battle 10
quote_text: How's this?

name: Battle 11
quote_text: You can count on me.

name: Battle 12
quote_text: Holler anytime you need backup!

name: Battle 13
quote_text: I always come through when it counts!

name: Battle 14
quote_text: Gahg!

name: Battle 15
quote_text: Sorry, this could be it for me...

name: Battle 16
quote_text: I'm ready to sling some magic power!

name: Battle 17
quote_text: It hurts all over...

name: Battle 18
quote_text: Well, what now?

name: Battle 19
quote_text: Okay, I'll give it all I've got!

name: Battle 20
quote_text: I'll give it all I've got!

name: Battle 21
quote_text: I'm your girl!

name: Battle 22
quote_text: I'm just happy to help.

name: Battle 23
quote_text: Nice work today!

name: Battle 24
quote_text: This is all my fault...

name: Battle 25
quote_text: This wasn't supposed to happen!

name: Battle 26
quote_text: Prepare yourself!

name: Battle 27
quote_text: Haaah!

name: Battle 28
quote_text: You're going to feel this!

name: Battle 29
quote_text: Let's end this here and now.

name: Battle 30
quote_text: Don't push yourself too hard, okay?

name: Battle 31
quote_text: Time to get back in the game!

name: Battle 32
quote_text: Blade of Wind!

name: Battle 33
quote_text: Whoa!

name: Battle 34
quote_text: I'll just have to try again.

name: Battle 35
quote_text: I'm all set over here.

name: Battle 36
quote_text: S-seriously?

name: Battle 37
quote_text: Is it my turn yet?

name: Battle 38
quote_text: Fine... But just this once, got it?

name: Rin 3 (Sun-soaked)
quote_text: Don't give me that look!

name: Rin 4 (Sun-soaked)
quote_text: I need to put some sunscreen on.

name: Rin 5 (Sun-soaked)
quote_text: I want to swim in the ocean!

name: Rin 6 (Sun-soaked)
quote_text: It's nice to play on the beach.

name: Rin 3 (Laundry Day)
quote_text: Your word is my command.

name: Rin 4 (Laundry Day)
quote_text: I'll clean up this mess!

name: Rin 5 (Laundry Day)
quote_text: It's always a pleasure, Master!

name: Rin 6 (Laundry Day)
quote_text: I won't do anything for Dust!

name: Battle 39
quote_text: Dark Detonation!

name: Battle 40
quote_text: I'll blast you to oblivion!

name: Rin 3 (Windstorm Kunoichi)
quote_text: Look, I'm a dangerous ninja!

name: Rin 4 (Windstorm Kunoichi)
quote_text: I feel like I'm some kind of bandit!

name: Rin 5 (Windstorm Kunoichi)
quote_text: This outfit is perfect for vanishing without a trace.

name: Rin 6 (Windstorm Kunoichi)
quote_text: Seems like a pretty conspicuous outfit for a ninja...

name: Rin 3 (Summer Sharpshooter)
quote_text: I think I'd like to look at some of the stalls.

name: Rin 4 (Summer Sharpshooter)
quote_text: I'll cool you off with my wind!

name: Rin 5 (Summer Sharpshooter)
quote_text: Listening to wind chimes is so calming...

name: Rin 6 (Summer Sharpshooter)
quote_text: I hope this hair accessory doesn't fall off.

name: Battle 41
quote_text: I could use this!

name: Battle 42
quote_text: Don't overdo it.

name: Battle 43
quote_text: I only need one blow!

name: Rin (Firepower is Key) 3
quote_text: You better watch out! I've got some serious firepower!

name: Rin (Firepower is Key) 4
quote_text: Wait here! I'll whip up something to eat!

name: Rin (Firepower is Key) 5
quote_text: I'll have some rice and veggies ready for you in just a minute!

name: Rin (Firepower is Key) 6
quote_text: No snacking before dinner!

name: Rin 3 (Class President)
quote_text: Gotta be careful not to be late.

name: Rin 4 (Class President)
quote_text: So, where's the troublemaker?

name: Rin 5 (Class President)
quote_text: School rules must be followed!

name: Rin 6 (Class President)
quote_text: Anything wrong with my outfit?

name: Rin 3 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: With this power… I will protect everyone.

name: Rin 4 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: I can't believe my movements are so light!

name: Rin 5 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: It might be more comfortable than usual.

name: Rin 6 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: It's incredible, I feel the power rushing through!

name: Rin (Everyone, It's Dinner Time) 3
quote_text: Now, shall we go?

name: Rin (Everyone, It's Dinner Time) 4
quote_text: Don't let your guard down.

name: Rin (Everyone, It's Dinner Time) 5
quote_text: Great, then let's eat!

name: Rin (Everyone, It's Dinner Time) 6
quote_text: You are so high maintenance.

name: Misc 1
quote_text: You're a nice guy, you know that?

name: Misc 2
quote_text: I'd say we've got a good thing going.

name: Misc 3
quote_text: *Sigh* Don't run me ragged. That's all I ask.

name: Misc 4
quote_text: My job class is wizard. Intermediate spells are my specialty.

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Kazuma's got a good handle on beginner-level magic.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: I lent Dust money AGAIN. *Sigh* That kind of investment has zero returns.

name: Misc 7
quote_text: J-just so you know... I'm fine with myself. Really.

name: Misc 8
quote_text: I'll use my magic to protect you!

name: Misc 9
quote_text: Megumin's explosion magic is really something to behold.

name: Misc 10
quote_text: Watch out for Dust, he's bona fide trash.

name: Misc 11
quote_text: Ignore him if he asks you for money or anything.

name: Misc 12
quote_text: Yunyun is really strong. Our party would only hold her back.

name: Misc 13
quote_text: I keep lending Dust money. How do I make myself stop?

name: Misc 14
quote_text: Kazuma makes me think knowing some beginner-level magic would be useful.

name: Misc 15
quote_text: Samuidoh's vegetables are the best. I'll think I'll buy some more from Amy.

name: Misc 16
quote_text: Goblins are a cakewalk, but beginner's banes are scary to take on solo.

name: Misc 17
quote_text: People always say bad things about Kazuma, but he's smart and reliable.

name: Misc 18
quote_text: I'm quite familiar with the jail... I've bailed Dust out countless times.

name: Misc 19
quote_text: Troublesome companions make quests twice as hard.

name: Misc 20
quote_text: Sorry, did Dust do something again?!

name: Misc 21
quote_text: I wish I could use powerful spells like the Crimson Demon Clan.

name: Misc 22
quote_text: Did Dust do something again? Sorry, I'll be right there!

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: Luna's chest is so large, and it looks so soft...

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: Hmph! Dust is an idiot! I will never help him again!

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: I know a shop that sells tasty veggies. Wanna go together?

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: Should I save up my skill points for some advanced magic?

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: Kazuma is friends with the princess... He's no ordinary guy.

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: Dust has good qualities too...somewhere. At least, I hope he does...

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: Kazuma actually uses his beginner level magic pretty effectively.

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: If you're ever in trouble, let me know! Many hands make light work!

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: Amy's rather...developed...don't you think? Could it be from all those Samuidoh veggies?

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: Since I've met Kazuma and Aqua, there's never a dull moment.

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: Maybe now I'll be able to help everyone out?

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: I'm no Crimson Demon, but I'm no pushover when it comes to magic power either!

name: Game Title 1
quote_text: God's Blessing on this Wonderful World! Fantastic Days

name: Game Title 2
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Game Title 3
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: *Sigh* Today I'd like to look after me and ONLY me. Is that too much to ask on my birthday?

name: Lia 1 (Dancing Adventurer)
quote_text: Performing and adventuring...I can't do without either one!

name: Lia 2 (Dancing Adventurer)
quote_text: Axel Hearts members are capable adventurers, too.

name: Lia 1 (Rising Idol)
quote_text: Striking a cute pose WHILE smiling? Now that's a tall order...

name: Lia 2 (Rising Idol)
quote_text: Do the fans even want me to go the "cute" route?

name: Lia 1 (Lancer)
quote_text: It occurs to me that my spear moves can be translated into dance.

name: Lia 2 (Lancer)
quote_text: I once entered a spear contest to see how my skills stack up... I ended up winning the thing.

name: Lia 1 (Casual)
quote_text: Let's stay in and take it easy today.

name: Lia 2 (Casual)
quote_text: There's nothing better than curling up with my beloved Konjiro.

name: Lia 1 (Beginner)
quote_text: More people need to know who we are.

name: Lia 2 (Beginner)
quote_text: I promise not to hold you back. So...can I join your party?

name: Lia 1 (Solo Photo Shoot)
quote_text: I care not for the sword—only for the lively dance of my spear!

name: Lia 2 (Solo Photo Shoot)
quote_text: Do you think I'll lose my fans if they see me fighting?

name: Lia 1 (Axel Hearts)
quote_text: Thanks for coming! We'll sing our hearts out for you!

name: Lia 2 (Axel Hearts)
quote_text: I sure hope the three of us can keep performing together.

name: Lia 1 (Midsummer Match)
quote_text: Now's my chance! Go ahead, try and return this ball if you can!

name: Lia 2 (Midsummer Match)
quote_text: I don't like losing, even if it's just a game. I'm going all-out!

name: Lia 1 (Marvelous Martial Arts)
quote_text: Hiii-yah! H-How was that? Martial arts are tough!

name: Lia 2 (Marvelous Martial Arts)
quote_text: Martial arts and dancing both require grace.

name: Lia 1 (Certified Kunoichi)
quote_text: A change of perspective makes such a difference. Even familiar scenery can be so pretty...

name: Lia 2 (Certified Kunoichi)
quote_text: Seeing a slice of Japanese culture here is quite strange.

name: Lia 1 (Amateur Pastry Chef)
quote_text: Have I ever given someone chocolate? That's a secret, hehe.

name: Lia 2 (Amateur Pastry Chef)
quote_text: I haven't made chocolate in forever. My friends and I used to swap them with each other.

name: Lia 1 (Dancing Announcer)
quote_text: Thank you for coming to the Axel Singing Contest!

name: Lia 2 (Dancing Announcer)
quote_text: As a dancer and your emcee today, I'll make sure you all have a wonderful time!

name: Lia 1 (Picture Day)
quote_text: Were the uniforms always this cute? It's kind of embarrassing.

name: Lia 2 (Picture Day)
quote_text: I can't wait for the day we can put on a sports festival in Axel.

name: Lia 1 (Maid for the Job)
quote_text: The warrior maid joins the battlefield! Ahem... I better hurry and finish these chores.

name: Lia 2 (Maid for the Job)
quote_text: Working as a maid sure is tough. It's more tiring than dance practice...

name: Lia (Beneath a Snowy Sky) 1
quote_text: I remember meeting up on a winter day like this, long ago. I was wearing something similar.

name: Lia (Beneath a Snowy Sky) 2
quote_text: Since I'm all dressed for the winter months, I guess I'll check out some shops I've never been to.

name: Lia (Fashionista Flair) 1
quote_text: Hehe. Wearing this reminds me of Japan.

name: Lia (Fashionista Flair) 2
quote_text: I used to go with a more sporty look on my days off. Would that be too much for this place?

name: Lia 1 (Sky After Rain)
quote_text: The rain stopped… Look, the sky's beatiful.

name: Lia 2 (Sky After Rain)
quote_text: I got all wet. But it's kind of refreshing.

name: Lia 1 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: I'm going to keep this awesome show going with these two…!

name: Lia 2 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Having come to this, I want to dress up Konjiro with matching outfits too.

name: Lia 1 (New Year's Melody)
quote_text: It kind of feels like New Year since the Magical keyboard sounds like a lyre, right?

name: Lia 2 (New Year's Melody)
quote_text: I’m glad because it looks like the Crimson Demons are also fond of New Year’s Day.

name: Lia 1 (Struggling Pastry Chef)
quote_text: It's a little crushed, but please accept... this chocolate expressing my gratitude!

name: Lia 2 (Struggling Pastry Chef)
quote_text: I should give the friendship chocolate to Cielo and Erika.

name: Lia (Tropical Taste) 1
quote_text: This place is great. It makes me want to sing a song.

name: Lia (Tropical Taste) 2
quote_text: This fresh taste... It really feels like we’re in the resort.

name: Lia (Let’s Trick Together) 1
quote_text: Happy Halloween! Even Konjiro is filled with determination tonight.

name: Lia (Let’s Trick Together) 2
quote_text: Are you ready, Konjiro? The chant is ‘Trick-or-treat’!

name: Lia (Dreamy Moment) 1
quote_text: Haha, what should we do for fun today, Konjiro?

name: Lia (Dreamy Moment) 2
quote_text: I will never forget Konjiro... Never.

name: Lia 1 (M, Master!)
quote_text: W-Welcome back, Master... Sigh, I never thought I’d be a maid again.

name: Lia 2 (M, Master!)
quote_text: Doing a show in a maid outfit... might not be so bad, surprisingly.

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: Thanks for everything, my fearless party leader. I'll be sure to pull my weight.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: I practice singing and dancing every day.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: Erika's got the cute act down pat. She's way better than me.

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: Men scare the living daylights out of Cielo. We really need to work on that.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: That was a productive day. I can't wait to go home to Konjiro.

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: Someday, I'll sing for a sold-out arena.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: Everyone's support is what got me this far.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: Oh no, you definitely don't want to stop by my place. It's a huge mess.

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: Want to see me perform? I'll send you an invitation to the next Axel Hearts concert.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: So...I wrote a new song. Mind giving me your opinion?

name: Greeting
quote_text: Ugh... I'm not the greatest at introductions.

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: I can be so much more!

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: I can always count on you. Thanks!

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: It's all about growing your fan base.

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: I try, but cleaning's not my strong suit.

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: The journey continues...

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: The team is what motivates me to transcend my limits.

name: Battle 1
quote_text: Stay sharp, team.

name: Battle 2
quote_text: I don't lose on stage OR the battlefield.

name: Battle 3
quote_text: Relax. You're with me now.

name: Battle 4
quote_text: Did I do well, Konjiro?

name: Battle 5
quote_text: But I'm still chasing my dream...

name: Battle 6
quote_text: No, not like this...

name: Battle 7
quote_text: Attack with the grace of a dancer!

name: Battle 8
quote_text: Aaagh!

name: Battle 9
quote_text: Ready to go?

name: Battle 10
quote_text: Give it up!

name: Battle 11
quote_text: It's okay. Stay calm.

name: Battle 12
quote_text: We'll get through this.

name: Battle 13
quote_text: I've got a song just for you.

name: Battle 14
quote_text: Aaagh!

name: Battle 15
quote_text: If I must go down, let it be on the stage...

name: Battle 16
quote_text: Time to take to the stage!

name: Battle 17
quote_text: Ugh, better pick up the slack...

name: Battle 18
quote_text: Any bright ideas?

name: Battle 19
quote_text: It's showtime!

name: Battle 20
quote_text: I will serve as the vanguard!

name: Battle 21
quote_text: Watch this, Konjiro!

name: Battle 22
quote_text: Thanks for believing in me.

name: Battle 23
quote_text: I may be a dancer, but I can fight, too!

name: Battle 24
quote_text: Konjiro, I'm sorry...

name: Battle 25
quote_text: I'll be sure to win next time!

name: Battle 26
quote_text: Hraaaaaah!

name: Battle 27
quote_text: Believe in yourself!

name: Battle 28
quote_text: I can't lose! Not until my dream comes true!

name: Battle 29
quote_text: Find just the right moment to strike!

name: Battle 30
quote_text: Leave it to me.

name: Battle 31
quote_text: I can feel your cheering in my heart.

name: Battle 32
quote_text: Prelude of Honor!

name: Battle 33
quote_text: Eeek!

name: Battle 34
quote_text: I can't be defeated...

name: Battle 35
quote_text: I'm ready to sing.

name: Battle 36
quote_text: I can still do this!

name: Battle 37
quote_text: What should I do?

name: Battle 38
quote_text: I want to be able to help everyone!

name: Lia 3 (Axel Hearts)
quote_text: I'm proud of this costume!

name: Lia 4 (Axel Hearts)
quote_text: I'm bad at cute poses.

name: Lia 5 (Axel Hearts)
quote_text: I wonder if that made everyone happy.

name: Lia 6 (Axel Hearts)
quote_text: Would you listen to my song?

name: Lia 3 (Marvelous Martial Arts)
quote_text: I think it's time for our new dance.

name: Lia 4 (Marvelous Martial Arts)
quote_text: Hraaah! Hroh!

name: Lia 5 (Marvelous Martial Arts)
quote_text: How do you like my spear?

name: Lia 6 (Marvelous Martial Arts)
quote_text: Hyaaah!

name: Battle 39
quote_text: Water Rhapsody!

name: Battle 40
quote_text: It's like dancing on water!

name: Lia 3 (Picture Day)
quote_text: I never thought I'd have to fight in a uniform like this.

name: Lia 4 (Picture Day)
quote_text: I pass for a high school student, right?

name: Lia 5 (Picture Day)
quote_text: Lalalaaa... ♪ Want to sing with me?

name: Lia 6 (Picture Day)
quote_text: That was a lot of exercise. Aren't you tired?

name: Battle 41
quote_text: That was a job well done.

name: Battle 42
quote_text: I'm still here, so don't give up!

name: Battle 43
quote_text: How refreshing!

name: Lia 3 (Maid for the Job)
quote_text: I am yours to command.

name: Lia 4 (Maid for the Job)
quote_text: Your command, my lord?

name: Lia 5 (Maid for the Job)
quote_text: All done. It's time for a break, I think.

name: Lia 6 (Maid for the Job)
quote_text: Who would've thought chores were such hard work...

name: Lia (Beneath a Snowy Sky) 3
quote_text: I kinda like the snow and cold.

name: Lia (Beneath a Snowy Sky) 4
quote_text: Watch out for the dry air.

name: Lia (Beneath a Snowy Sky) 5
quote_text: Behold the magnificent Konjiro!

name: Lia (Beneath a Snowy Sky) 6
quote_text: My throat...? It's fine.

name: Lia (Fashionista Flair) 3
quote_text: I want you to see the real me.

name: Lia (Fashionista Flair) 4
quote_text: I feel a little silly wearing this...

name: Lia (Fashionista Flair) 5
quote_text: It's just like the old days.

name: Lia (Fashionista Flair) 6
quote_text: This is so comfortable to move in!

name: Lia 3 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: I'm going to make this the best show!

name: Lia 4 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: I'm always a dancer.

name: Lia 5 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Thank you! I'm glad you enjoyed it!

name: Lia 6 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Whew… Can we finally take a breather?

name: Lia 3 (Struggling Pastry Chef)
quote_text: I have something I want to give to you.

name: Lia 4 (Struggling Pastry Chef)
quote_text: I remember when I was lived in Japan.

name: Lia 5 (Struggling Pastry Chef)
quote_text: Should we take a quick rest?

name: Lia 6 (Struggling Pastry Chef)
quote_text: Happy Valentine's Day.

name: Lia (Tropical Taste) 3
quote_text: Playing in the water under the night sky. This is great.

name: Lia (Tropical Taste) 4
quote_text: An outdoor performance might be great as well.

name: Lia (Tropical Taste) 5
quote_text: Can I sing a song?

name: Lia (Tropical Taste) 6
quote_text: It’s highly functional.

name: Lia (Let’s Trick Together) 3
quote_text: Let's begin the Halloween show!

name: Lia (Let’s Trick Together) 4
quote_text: Now, let’s surprise everyone!

name: Lia (Let’s Trick Together) 5
quote_text: I’m going to prank you! What do you think?!

name: Lia (Let’s Trick Together) 6
quote_text: Let’s gather more snacks!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: Give my song a listen, will you?

name: Misc 2
quote_text: It's uncanny! Every second with you is exciting.

name: Misc 3
quote_text: Axel Hearts performs at venues all over town.

name: Misc 4
quote_text: I'd love to see you at our next show.

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Konjiro's going to love my tales of adventure today.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: I know it's for the fans, but these smiling poses? Not my specialty.

name: Misc 7
quote_text: I'm pretty good with a spear, y'know? Lanced my way to first in a martial arts tournament.

name: Misc 8
quote_text: Tomorrow's the big show. We should take a break from practice.

name: Misc 9
quote_text: I was in the naginata club. That's why I'm good with spears.

name: Misc 10
quote_text: I'm honored that Princess Iris has heard of Axel Hearts.

name: Misc 11
quote_text: It's a little sad that people don't believe Aqua is actually a goddess.

name: Misc 12
quote_text: Talking with Konjiro helps me relax. He's a true friend.

name: Misc 13
quote_text: Kazuma takes really good care of us as our producer.

name: Misc 14
quote_text: People say my room is a mess, but I know where everything is.

name: Misc 15
quote_text: As the leader of Axel Hearts, I have to always be at my best.

name: Misc 16
quote_text: I hope I will always be able to dance with Cielo and Erika.

name: Misc 17
quote_text: Sorry... I'm, um, not very good at keeping my room clean.

name: Misc 18
quote_text: As a dancer, my fans are more precious than anything.

name: Misc 19
quote_text: I composed every single Axel Hearts song.

name: Misc 20
quote_text: Aqua is an excellent performer. I want to learn some of her tricks.

name: Misc 21
quote_text: Konjiro was the first friend who helped me when I was alone.

name: Misc 22
quote_text: I wonder if Yunyun would want to be friends with Konjiro...

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: My naginata skills helped me win a spear tournament, too.

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: Erika's selfishness sure is a pain...

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: Konjiro must be lonely. I should find him some friends.

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: Our songs are always upbeat, but I'd like to try a ballad.

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: Aqua is really talented. I bet she'd be a good dancer, too.

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: I trained with Cielo once. It got a bit out of hand, to tell true.

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: I practice my singing and dancing daily. Wouldn't want to disappoint the fans, after all.

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: Vanir offered one of his dolls as a friend for Konjiro, but I obviously refused him.

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: I wonder if I should try to be more fashionable... I'll ask Erika later.

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: I've made up my mind! My place is here with Cielo and Erika in Axel Hearts!

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: I feel as if my singing is better than ever!

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: With each trial I overcome, I can feel my strength grow.

name: Game Title 1
quote_text: God's Blessing on this Wonderful World! Fantastic Days

name: Game Title 2
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Game Title 3
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: My birthday is also the birthday of the Axel Hearts. Thanks for remembering.

name: Cielo 1 (Dancing Adventurer)
quote_text: I-it's nothing personal, but I can't deal with men. My fists start flying on their own...

name: Cielo 2 (Dancing Adventurer)
quote_text: I want to bring Axel Hearts to the whole wide world!

name: Cielo 1 (Androphobe)
quote_text: C-come any closer, and you'll be seeing stars!

name: Cielo 2 (Androphobe)
quote_text: Thanks for the compliment, but I've never considered myself attractive.

name: Cielo 1 (Arch Priest)
quote_text: I'm better versed in magic than hand-to-hand combat!

name: Cielo 2 (Arch Priest)
quote_text: I'm a pro at healing magic. Feel free to get mangled out there!

name: Cielo 1 (Casual)
quote_text: Get too close, and I might hurt you...

name: Cielo 2 (Casual)
quote_text: On my days off, I like to go...anywhere men aren't.

name: Cielo 1 (Beginner)
quote_text: My personality's a character flaw I'm hoping to fix.

name: Cielo 2 (Beginner)
quote_text: I never cared much for the nobility.

name: Cielo 1 (Moonlit Stage)
quote_text: This is fun, but someday I want to dance on the big stage.

name: Cielo 2 (Moonlit Stage)
quote_text: The only thing I'm good at is dancing, but that's also when I'm happiest.

name: Cielo 1 (Axel Hearts)
quote_text: I promise to do my very best, so please enjoy my performance!

name: Cielo 2 (Axel Hearts)
quote_text: Seeing people enjoy my dancing makes me so glad I became a dancer.

name: Cielo 1 (Strict Teacher)
quote_text: It's important to start with the basics! Let's practice, Amy!

name: Cielo 2 (Strict Teacher)
quote_text: Get up! I know you can take more than that!

name: Cielo 1 (Maid in Training)
quote_text: I'll work hard to become a proper maid!

name: Cielo 2 (Maid in Training)
quote_text: Phew...finally done. I need to thank my maids back home.

name: Cielo 1 (Fun Sleepover)
quote_text: I bet every day would be lively if I had a little sister like Mia.

name: Cielo 2 (Fun Sleepover)
quote_text: My hair gets tangled easily, so I make sure it's dry before going to bed.

name: Cielo 1 (Exciting Magic)
quote_text: My heart is b-beating so quickly... Is this what they call "the magic of love"?

name: Cielo 2 (Exciting Magic)
quote_text: Whenever I catch a glimpse of Kazuma I start to burn up... S-Stay away from me!

name: Cielo 1 (Summer Explorer)
quote_text: Are you thirsty? Here, have some of this coconut juice!

name: Cielo 2 (Summer Explorer)
quote_text: I-I'm not too confident in the water... Any chance you could teach me how to swim?

name: Cielo 1 (Faith in Your Fists)
quote_text: Training never lies! Ineffective punches are a sign that you're not working hard enough!

name: Cielo 2 (Faith in Your Fists)
quote_text: Father's fists are truly something else. I have much to learn before I can match him.

name: Cielo (Warmhearted) 1
quote_text: Hot springs do wonders for your skin. Any dancer worth their dancing shoes knows that!

name: Cielo (Warmhearted) 2
quote_text: Hot springs rejuvenate the mind and body so you're ready for whatever comes next, like tomorrow's training!

name: Cielo 1 (After School)
quote_text: My fatigue disappears when we play together.

name: Cielo 2 (After School)
quote_text: Strict rules allow us to develop physically and mentally!

name: Cielo 1 (Beneath the Stars)
quote_text: Summer night's sky is beautiful when you see it from a dark place!

name: Cielo 2 (Beneath the Stars)
quote_text: The 3 of us camping together feels new. Even if we're always together....

name: Cielo 1 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: We have to practice real hard for the people who support us.

name: Cielo 2 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Tell me, tell me Cielo... Get to know more about me.

name: Cielo 1 (Mysterious Warning)
quote_text: I can't believe you have to send out the invitations as well, your work is quite difficult...

name: Cielo 2 (Mysterious Warning)
quote_text: W-Why are they coming after my gloves...?

name: Cielo (Autumn Breeze) 1
quote_text: Handshakes and pictures are all welcome! Y-You don't have to be so scared-meow...!

name: Cielo (Autumn Breeze) 2
quote_text: Umm... Whether it's serving or dancing, I will try my best-meow...!

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: J-just glad to be on board!

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: I dance to overcome my fear of men.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: I have a feeling my martial arts background helps me dance.

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: I can't thank Kazuma enough for giving me a place in this party.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: Those who want a handshake...please wear gloves.

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: Someday, the girls and I will score a super huge gig.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: Let me know if you're ever wounded. I'm an arch priestess, after all.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: You want to learn martial arts from me? Sure, but be warned...I'm a strict teacher.

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: My little brother is to be our family's successor, which frees me to walk my own path.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: I've never had a boyfriend. Maybe because I manhandle every guy who comes near me.

name: Greeting
quote_text: I-if you're a man, I suggest you don't touch me.

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: I feel stronger now.

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: All that training is paying off.

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: I have to up my game as an arch priest!

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: The party comes first!

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: Limits are meant to be broken!

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: I'm an Axel Hearts member too, you know?

name: Battle 1
quote_text: Together, we can do anything!

name: Battle 2
quote_text: I-if you're a man, keep your distance!

name: Battle 3
quote_text: Guess who? Guess who? It's Cielo!

name: Battle 4
quote_text: This is my victory dance!

name: Battle 5
quote_text: Sorry... I screwed up.

name: Battle 6
quote_text: I wanted to perform one last time, at least...

name: Battle 7
quote_text: No, stay baaaack!

name: Battle 8
quote_text: Hi-yah!

name: Battle 9
quote_text: Here goes nothing.

name: Battle 10
quote_text: Noooooo!

name: Battle 11
quote_text: I'm here to help.

name: Battle 12
quote_text: Are you okay?

name: Battle 13
quote_text: I-I can help too, you know?

name: Battle 14
quote_text: Nnngh...

name: Battle 15
quote_text: Sorry I'm such a klutz...

name: Battle 16
quote_text: I'm all set to go!

name: Battle 17
quote_text: I must keep going...

name: Battle 18
quote_text: Oh, this is quite a pickle...

name: Battle 19
quote_text: A-any males...better keep your distance from me.

name: Battle 20
quote_text: Are we going to be okay...?

name: Battle 21
quote_text: This is all so I can stand on stage!

name: Battle 22
quote_text: Did I prove helpful?

name: Battle 23
quote_text: I couldn't have won without all of you.

name: Battle 24
quote_text: I'm sorry I couldn't do more...

name: Battle 25
quote_text: I have to become stronger.

name: Battle 26
quote_text: Please stop!

name: Battle 27
quote_text: I'll do my best!

name: Battle 28
quote_text: Don't come any closer!

name: Battle 29
quote_text: Hraaagh!

name: Battle 30
quote_text: Time for the arch priestess!

name: Battle 31
quote_text: I'll handle this!

name: Battle 32
quote_text: Sacred Highness Heal!

name: Battle 33
quote_text: It hurts...

name: Battle 34
quote_text: I can't believe I lost...

name: Battle 35
quote_text: I-I'm ready anytime!

name: Battle 36
quote_text: Are we going to be okay?

name: Battle 37
quote_text: Have I been forgotten?

name: Battle 38
quote_text: Guess what? It's Cielo's turn!

name: Cielo 3 (Axel Hearts)
quote_text: I'm confident in my dance skills.

name: Cielo 4 (Axel Hearts)
quote_text: My practice will finally pay off!

name: Cielo 5 (Axel Hearts)
quote_text: Thanks for your support!

name: Cielo 6 (Axel Hearts)
quote_text: Our singing and dancing will make everyone smile!

name: Cielo 3 (Maid in Training)
quote_text: Mustn't hit Master...

name: Cielo 4 (Maid in Training)
quote_text: I will serve you today.

name: Cielo 5 (Maid in Training)
quote_text: It's hard work being a maid.

name: Cielo 6 (Maid in Training)
quote_text: Ah, are my clothes dirty?

name: Cielo 3 (Fun Sleepover)
quote_text: I-I'm sorry about the outfit!

name: Cielo 4 (Fun Sleepover)
quote_text: My pajamas only fuel my determination!

name: Cielo 5 (Fun Sleepover)
quote_text: How about a glass of warm milk?

name: Cielo 6 (Fun Sleepover)
quote_text: I wish you sweet dreams.

name: Battle 39
quote_text: Wind Rondo!

name: Battle 40
quote_text: Glide across the sky!

name: Cielo 3 (Summer Explorer)
quote_text: H-How do I look in this swimsuit?

name: Cielo 4 (Summer Explorer)
quote_text: I'm not a good swimmer...

name: Cielo 5 (Summer Explorer)
quote_text: Whew, I'm— Is that watermelon?

name: Cielo 6 (Summer Explorer)
quote_text: L-Look the other way, will you!

name: Battle 41
quote_text: D-Did that do anything...?

name: Battle 42
quote_text: I'll cheer you on!

name: Battle 43
quote_text: Thank you, I'm feeling better.

name: Cielo (Warmhearted) 3
quote_text: We need to work on making ourselves happy!

name: Cielo (Warmhearted) 4
quote_text: Nothing like a hot spring to make your skin soft!

name: Cielo (Warmhearted) 5
quote_text: Rest is an integral part of any training regimen.

name: Cielo (Warmhearted) 6
quote_text: Just seeing if I look suitably toned in this.

name: Cielo 3 (After School)
quote_text: Get up and go to school!

name: Cielo 4 (After School)
quote_text: How have  you been?

name: Cielo 5 (After School)
quote_text: Hehe, such a nice weather.

name: Cielo 6 (After School)
quote_text: Can you see under my skirt?

name: Cielo 3 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: I'm pumped!

name: Cielo 4 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Fists seem okay too.

name: Cielo 5 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Hurray! They did it!

name: Cielo 6 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: I'd like to make myself known.

name: Cielo (Autumn Breeze) 3
quote_text: What would you like to order-meow?

name: Cielo (Autumn Breeze) 4
quote_text: Bad customers can go back-meow.

name: Cielo (Autumn Breeze) 5
quote_text: This is a victory dance...Meow♪

name: Cielo (Autumn Breeze) 6
quote_text: Serving... Did I get used to it-meow?

name: Misc 1
quote_text: Th-thanks a bunch.

name: Misc 2
quote_text: I-I'm not cute! Not in the slightest...

name: Misc 3
quote_text: Thanks for supporting Axel Hearts.

name: Misc 4
quote_text: I'm going to be the world's first dancing arch priest!

name: Misc 5
quote_text: You can catch Axel Hearts at a venue near you.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: My parents wanted me to grow up strong, so I've been learning martial arts all my life.

name: Misc 7
quote_text: Though I can't hold a candle to Aqua, I have a pretty good grasp of recovery spells.

name: Misc 8
quote_text: Sleeping in that mountain of trash is so like you, Lia.

name: Misc 9
quote_text: I may be a noble, but inside I am just as regular as you. Please, no special treatment.

name: Misc 10
quote_text: I was raised as a boy and learned how to fight.

name: Misc 11
quote_text: There are a lot of girls out there working as dancers.

name: Misc 12
quote_text: I'll hit you if you touch me, so let's use practice swords.

name: Misc 13
quote_text: I want to learn to be as straightforward as Erika is.

name: Misc 14
quote_text: Meeting Erika and Lia was a real turning point in my life.

name: Misc 15
quote_text: You need to know how to say no, but it's hard for me.

name: Misc 16
quote_text: If you want to learn how to fight, just ask me.

name: Misc 17
quote_text: I began dancing to overcome my shyness... Is it working?

name: Misc 18
quote_text: Did you know that I do all the choreography for Axel Hearts?

name: Misc 19
quote_text: Does Darkness also get yelled at for being an adventuring noble?

name: Misc 20
quote_text: I'm sorry, Kazuma! Are you hurt? Here, let me cast a healing spell!

name: Misc 21
quote_text: Kazuma is always working to cure me of my fear of men.

name: Misc 22
quote_text: Boys used to pick on me when I was younger, so I'm afraid of them now.

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: I-if there's anything I can do to help, I'll do it!

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: Handshake events... W-will I have to shake hands with men, too?!

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: Darkness is also from a noble family. It's hard for us.

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: Worries? I deal with them by working out! Give it a try!

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: I don't want to live a sheltered life just because I was born a noble.

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: We're not the only group out there, which is why we've got to stay on top of our game.

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: Aqua's martial arts skills are amazing. I need to ask her where she learned her moves.

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: Maybe I should use fewer gloves at the next meet-and-greet... No, I don't think I can!

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: I can't even entertain the idea of marriage. I've dedicated myself to Axel Hearts.

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: I hope that Axel Hearts stays together for a long time.

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: The tougher the training, the tougher I get!

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: Thank you for letting me train with you, sir!

name: Game Title 1
quote_text: God's Blessing on this Wonderful World! Fantastic Days

name: Game Title 2
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Game Title 3
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: I, uh...won't let the team down. Promise!

name: Erika 1 (Dancing Adventurer)
quote_text: All the world will know my beauty!

name: Erika 2 (Dancing Adventurer)
quote_text: Would you LOOK at these side ponytails swaying in the wind? I just...can't even!

name: Erika 1 (Fan Service)
quote_text: Oh... I SUPPOSE I could spare a minute.

name: Erika 2 (Fan Service)
quote_text: See? Complimenting me is well worth it.

name: Erika 1 (Ranger)
quote_text: This dagger is the cutest thing ever! Well, second-cutest.

name: Erika 2 (Ranger)
quote_text: I'm just as strong as I am cute. You'll see!

name: Erika 1 (Casual)
quote_text: I'm the cuteness authority!

name: Erika 2 (Casual)
quote_text: It's getting hot in here. Could it be because all eyes are on me?

name: Erika 1 (Beginner)
quote_text: Wait, I know what you're thinking. I'm cute, right?

name: Erika 2 (Beginner)
quote_text: You should be happy! Questing with me is a rare and sought-after honor!

name: Erika 1 (Axel Hearts)
quote_text: No blinking allowed during my shows! All eyes on me!

name: Erika 2 (Axel Hearts)
quote_text: My cuteness has no limits! I'll just keep getting cuter and cuter!

name: Erika 1 (Make Me Look Cute)
quote_text: Take a photo when you're ready! Make sure to capture the moment!

name: Erika 2 (Make Me Look Cute)
quote_text: What's my best angle? From the front? The side? Let's get both!

name: Erika 1 (Martial Arts Shoot)
quote_text: No one can pose as cutely or coolly as me!

name: Erika 2 (Martial Arts Shoot)
quote_text: Get your cameras ready, here comes my cutest pose yet!

name: Erika 1 (Cute Klutz)
quote_text: Eek! I don't think I can stand! But that's endearing, right?

name: Erika 2 (Cute Klutz)
quote_text: A layer of ice only makes me shine brighter! The attention is a little embarrassing, though!

name: Erika 1 (Extra Girly)
quote_text: I'm already so cute. I can't imagine what would happen if my skin became even more beautiful.

name: Erika 2 (Extra Girly)
quote_text: I never knew lemons were good for your skin! I'll need to thank Amy.

name: Erika 1 (Tsundere Friend)
quote_text: Oh no, I'm running late... Eek! Watch where you're going!

name: Erika 2 (Tsundere Friend)
quote_text: Don't you think, like, I'm the cutest in the class—no, the universe even?

name: Erika 1 (Secret Getaway)
quote_text: I'm incognito today. Don't make a fuss just because my swimsuit is super cute.

name: Erika 2 (Secret Getaway)
quote_text: I'm a very good swimmer. In fact, people might mistake me for a mermaid.

name: Erika (Devilish Dancer) 1
quote_text: Happy Halloween! This is an cute gift from the even cuter me!

name: Erika (Devilish Dancer) 2
quote_text: Trick-or-cute! Go on! Call me cute or I'll play a trick on you!

name: Erika (Cuteness Triumph) 1
quote_text: Cuteness is power! And since I'm the cutest, I'm also the strongest!

name: Erika (Cuteness Triumph) 2
quote_text: Let's see how her explosion magic handles the explosive power of my cuteness!

name: Erika (Cute n' Sweet) 1
quote_text: I'm the cutest girl in the world, so I'm going to make you the world's cutest chocolates!

name: Erika (Cute n' Sweet) 2
quote_text: Look at this chocolate! Isn't it cute? But not as cute as I am, of course!

name: Erika 1 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Erika is still much cuter! It's hard to miss that!

name: Erika 2 (Legendary Adventurer)
quote_text: Don't you wanna reach the other side of cuteness with me?

name: Erika 1 (Cute Investigation)
quote_text: They say that you can go through anything for cuteness.

name: Erika 2 (Cute Investigation)
quote_text: I'm gonna get more famous and get the whole world's attention!

name: Erika (Piercing The Heart) 1
quote_text: Hello~! I’m Erika, the cutest in Axel's Angel Squad!

name: Erika (Piercing The Heart) 2
quote_text: Now, now! Any of you who want to get treated by me, stand in line!

name: Erika 1 (Snowball-Hurling Starlet)
quote_text: You are SO going down! Get ready to eat snow, with a side order of cuteness!

name: Erika 2 (Snowball-Hurling Starlet)
quote_text: Snowball fight! Winner takes home the prize. Who's ready?

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: You're lucky to be in the same party as someone as cute as me.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: Did someone say "cute"? I can only assume you're talking about me!

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: I'm cute AND a competent ranger. How's that for a double threat?

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: Uh, why'd you touch me? Because I'm cute? ...I knew it!

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: So, on a scale of one to a hundred, how cute am I? C'mon, tell me!

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: Lia and Cielo are cute too. After me, of course.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: Hey, I think I'm cuter than I was yesterday. What do I do? It won't stop!

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: The cuter I get, the more likely it is Mom and Dad will notice me.

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: I know that look. You've only got eyes for me.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: You want me all to yourself? That won't fly...I belong to all my fans.

name: Greeting
quote_text: 1,000% pure cuteness? That's me, Erika!

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: No way! I'm even cuter than before!

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: It's a sin to be this cute!

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: Yep, I'm too cute for my own good.

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: I'm so cute, it scares me!

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: My beauty knows no bounds!

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: Onward, to new heights of cuteness!

name: Battle 1
quote_text: Being unbearably cute is a 24/7 job!

name: Battle 2
quote_text: You want a handshake? Where's your ticket?

name: Battle 3
quote_text: 1000% pure cuteness right here.

name: Battle 4
quote_text: Cuteness triumphs over all.

name: Battle 5
quote_text: So long as my cuteness remains, I still win...

name: Battle 6
quote_text: How dare you hurt a girl! Especially one this cute...

name: Battle 7
quote_text: I'm always cute! Even when fighting!

name: Battle 8
quote_text: Take that!

name: Battle 9
quote_text: You'll fall for me soon enough!

name: Battle 10
quote_text: I'm mounting a direct assault...on your heart!

name: Battle 11
quote_text: Now, everyone pay attention!

name: Battle 12
quote_text: You look like you've seen an angel.

name: Battle 13
quote_text: Who's the cutest in the world? Me, obviously!

name: Battle 14
quote_text: Owie.

name: Battle 15
quote_text: If I'm gonna die, at least let me fix my makeup first!

name: Battle 16
quote_text: All eyes on Erika!

name: Battle 17
quote_text: I'm super cute, even in rags!

name: Battle 18
quote_text: Cast your gaze on me and me alone.

name: Battle 19
quote_text: Beauty queen here!

name: Battle 20
quote_text: All eyes on me!

name: Battle 21
quote_text: It's me, Erika! I'm so cute, it's blinding!

name: Battle 22
quote_text: Cute girls can fight too!

name: Battle 23
quote_text: That's what you get for messing with me!

name: Battle 24
quote_text: How could someone so cute lose...?

name: Battle 25
quote_text: Try not to fall for my tear-streaked face.

name: Mia 1 (Mischievous Beastman)

name: Mia 2 (Mischievous Beastman)

name: Mia 1 (Endless Eater)

name: Mia 2 (Endless Eater)

name: Mia 1 (Lancer)

name: Mia 2 (Lancer)

name: Mia 1 (Casual)

name: Mia 2 (Casual)

name: Mia 1 (Beginner)

name: Mia 2 (Beginner)
quote_text: Wow, there's so much to do out here! I love the adventurer's life!

name: Mia 1 (Harried Housekeeper)
quote_text: Spick-and-span's the name o' the game!

name: Mia 2 (Harried Housekeeper)

name: Mia 1 (Yummy Quest)
quote_text: *Nom nom* Mm, this sauce you made is super tasty, Kazuma!

name: Mia 2 (Yummy Quest)
quote_text: Grilled squid on the beach is the best! I can't wait for Amy to try it!

name: Mia 1 (Kunoichi)
quote_text: Hi-yah! I'm a ninja, startin' today! You'll never see me comin'!

name: Mia 2 (Kunoichi)
quote_text: Kazuma told me ninjas are super strong! That's why I'm gonna be one!

name: Mia 2 (Insatiable Santa)
quote_text: Say, Kazuma, when's the next Christmas? Can it be tomorrow?! Or the day after, maybe?!

name: Mia 1 (Pillow Fighter)
quote_text: Sleepovers mean pillow fights! Eat Mia's supersonic pillow!

name: Mia 2 (Pillow Fighter)
quote_text: I'm not even a little tired! I'm...going to stay up all night and... Zzz...

name: Mia 2 (Meat Bun Master)

name: Mia 2 (Harvest Dance)

quote_text: Fried squid, takoyaki, apple candy... This festival has so many tasty treats!

name: Mia 2 (Food Stall Frenzy)
quote_text: It's kinda long, but it feels super cool to wear! I'm startin' to like these yukata!

quote_text: Trick-or-treat! Candy is nice, but I'd rather get delicious meat!

name: Mia (Glowing Pumpkin) 2
quote_text: I was puttin' up Halloween decorations with Amy! Whaddya think? Cute, huh?

quote_text: I was so cold playin' in the snow alone, but with friends? It's suddenly warm!

name: Mia (Silly Snow Day) 2
quote_text: I'll show you lots of ways to have fun on a snowy day!
