quote_text: Sniff... sniff... I can smell the evidence, the truth is in front of my eyes!

name: Mia (Diligent Investigation) 2
quote_text: We will take care of every difficult task such as looking for cats or running errands!

name: Mia (So Sleepy) 1
quote_text: Ah, it’s so bothersome... Somebody carry me on your back...

name: Mia (So Sleepy) 2
quote_text: *Roll*... Can Mia just live here...?

name: Mia 3 (Harried Housekeeper)
quote_text: Time to get cleanin'!

name: Mia 4 (Harried Housekeeper)
quote_text: Outta my way!

name: Mia 5 (Harried Housekeeper)
quote_text: Leave the maid work to me!

name: Mia 3 (Kunoichi)
quote_text: You'll never see a nimbler ninja than me!

name: Mia 4 (Kunoichi)
quote_text: Do you think I'll be good at ninjutsu?

name: Mia 5 (Kunoichi)
quote_text: I'm a ninjutsu! ...Did I say that right?

name: Mia 6 (Kunoichi)
quote_text: I'm hungry... Time to sneak a snack!

name: Mia 3 (Pillow Fighter)
quote_text: It's a pajama party!

name: Mia 4 (Pillow Fighter)
quote_text: Ahahaha! Pillow fiiight!!!

name: Mia 5 (Pillow Fighter)
quote_text: *Yawn* Zzz... Zzz...

name: Mia 6 (Pillow Fighter)
quote_text: I'm not even a little tired!

name: Battle 39
quote_text: Melon Bomber!

name: Battle 40
quote_text: I'm the king of fruit!

name: Mia 3 (Harvest Dance)
quote_text: I'm a cut above!

name: Mia 4 (Harvest Dance)
quote_text: Hey, I can really move in this thing!

name: Mia 5 (Harvest Dance)
quote_text: It's time for my victory dance! Yaaay!

name: Mia 6 (Harvest Dance)
quote_text: Come on, let's celebrate!

name: Battle 41
quote_text: Pretty impressive!

name: Battle 42
quote_text: Anyone want veggies?

name: Battle 43
quote_text: All right, back on my feet!

name: Mia (Glowing Pumpkin) 3
quote_text: Gimme food or I'll play a trick on you!

name: Mia (Glowing Pumpkin) 4
quote_text: Gimme cake! And a pie while you're at it!

name: Mia (Glowing Pumpkin) 5
quote_text: I'm gonna eat pumpkin candy when I get home!

name: Mia (Glowing Pumpkin) 6
quote_text: Gimme your pumpkins!

name: Mia (Silly Snow Day) 3
quote_text: Winter really suits me!

name: Mia (Silly Snow Day) 4
quote_text: Let's work out to warm up!

name: Mia (Silly Snow Day) 5
quote_text: Frozen cabbage tastes delicious!

name: Mia (Silly Snow Day) 6
quote_text: This outfit keeps me snug and warm!

name: Mia 3 (Desert Trip)
quote_text: Where's the desert treasure~!

name: Mia 4 (Desert Trip)
quote_text: I'll do my best at the desert~!

name: Mia 5 (Desert Trip)
quote_text: A golden cabbage, looks delicious!

name: Mia 6 (Desert Trip)
quote_text: I'm not bothered by the heat!

name: Mia 3 (Vegetable Party)
quote_text: I will show you my power!

name: Mia 4 (Vegetable Party)
quote_text: Keep it up!

name: Mia 5 (Vegetable Party)
quote_text: I wonder if there are any tasty vegetables.

name: Mia 6 (Vegetable Party)
quote_text: I’ve gotten hungry...

name: Mia (Diligent Investigation) 3
quote_text: Clues are obtained by going out and running around!

name: Mia (Diligent Investigation) 4
quote_text: Take my reasoning

name: Mia (Diligent Investigation) 5
quote_text: I won’t lose a single clue!

name: Mia (Diligent Investigation) 6
quote_text: You are the culprit!

name: Mia 6 (Harried Housekeeper)
quote_text: Always gotta clean up after a fight!

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: Teach me anything an' everything about the world!

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: I'll make piles o' coin...and then feast like a king!

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: Amy's always there for me. She's like my big sis!

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: We farm oodles of veggies back up north!

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: Forget the greens, gimme meat any day!

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: Get your veggies right here! Big sale!

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: Amy's so cute! Ooh, I just love her to bits!

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: You're giving me your meat bun? That's awfully swell!

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: I really aced it today, and then some! How about a head pat, huh?

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: Ol' Mia's got your back to the bitter end!

name: Greeting
quote_text: There's a wide world out there, jam-packed with tasty morsels!

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: Delicious eats make me strong!

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: I'm just gettin' started!

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: Check it out. I'm even stronger now!

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: I bet this'll earn me a compliment from Amy!

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: Mia here, ready and rarin' to go!

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: I'm a growing girl, y'know?

name: Battle 1
quote_text: I'm ready for action!

name: Battle 2
quote_text: Let's put these baddies away and celebrate with a steak!

name: Battle 3
quote_text: Amy's gonna lo-ove hearin' about this!

name: Battle 4
quote_text: Buh-bye!

name: Battle 5
quote_text: Yeesh. Can I go home?

name: Battle 6
quote_text: Boy, I am famished!

name: Battle 7
quote_text: This is beastly strength!

name: Battle 8
quote_text: Hi-yah!

name: Battle 9
quote_text: This'll really hurt!

name: Battle 10
quote_text: Last chance to surrender!

name: Battle 11
quote_text: Better load up on meat an' veggies!

name: Battle 12
quote_text: I got this!

name: Battle 13
quote_text: Oh yeah! I am pumped!

name: Battle 14
quote_text: Owie...

name: Battle 15
quote_text: Amy, help me...

name: Battle 16
quote_text: Let's do this!

name: Battle 17
quote_text: I'm too hungry to move...

name: Battle 18
quote_text: Better keep them dukes up!

name: Battle 19
quote_text: Here I come!

name: Battle 20
quote_text: This is how it's done!

name: Battle 21
quote_text: I'm pretty strong, you know!

name: Battle 22
quote_text: I did it! Show me the meat!

name: Battle 23
quote_text: Did you see that?

name: Battle 24
quote_text: I lost...

name: Battle 25
quote_text: I'm going to grow even stronger.

name: Battle 26
quote_text: Aaagh!

name: Battle 27
quote_text: I'm gonna eat you!

name: Battle 28
quote_text: I can do anything if I try!

name: Battle 29
quote_text: Hyaaahhh!!

name: Battle 30
quote_text: Beastman veggies sure are tasty.

name: Battle 31
quote_text: Don't worry, I'll save you!

name: Battle 32
quote_text: Boulder Bomber!

name: Battle 33
quote_text: Hyaaah!

name: Battle 34
quote_text: I can't go on...

name: Battle 35
quote_text: All ready to go!

name: Battle 36
quote_text: I want meat for dinner...

name: Battle 37
quote_text: Let me at 'em!

name: Battle 38
quote_text: I'm in the mood for something tasty!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: Y'know, you're pretty cute. Wanna take home some veggies?

name: Misc 2
quote_text: You and Amy are the best!

name: Misc 3
quote_text: We beastmen grow the tastiest veggies around, y'know?

name: Misc 4
quote_text: Veggies can wait. Bring on the meat!

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Anyone seen Amy? I get worried when she's not around.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: Mia's m'name. A northern beastman, born 'n' bred. Rawr!

name: Misc 7
quote_text: Ooh, I am ITCHIN' for some action. Let's hit the road already!

name: Misc 8
quote_text: Kazuma! Teach me how to make meat buns!

name: Misc 9
quote_text: What's for dinner, Amy? I'll do the shopping for you!

name: Misc 10
quote_text: Yunyun is always by herself. Do you think she's lonely?

name: Misc 11
quote_text: That looks fun! Let me give it a try!

name: Misc 12
quote_text: I'm heading home... Amy wants me back early today.

name: Misc 13
quote_text: Ugh... Sitting still is so hard.

name: Misc 14
quote_text: Aqua! Do that magic with the squirting water for me!

name: Misc 15
quote_text: Beastman veggies are the best. Try this corn I grew!

name: Misc 16
quote_text: My dream is to eat tasty stuff all over the world!

name: Misc 17
quote_text: Yummy! What is this? I want Amy to try it, too.

name: Misc 18
quote_text: Do you wanna play with me, Yunyun? It's no fun being alone.

name: Misc 19
quote_text: We have nothing but veggies back home, so I want meat!

name: Misc 20
quote_text: Kazuma is like my big brother, and Amy is like my big sister!

name: Misc 21
quote_text: Wanna climb trees with me? Let's see who gets higher!

name: Misc 22
quote_text: Wanna play with me? I'm fine with either tag or hide-and-seek!

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: I'm hungry... Are there any meat buns around? Maybe?

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: Eating nothing but vegetables all the time gets boring. I want meat!

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: Yunyun gives me snacks and she plays with me! I like her!

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: Wiz and Amy both have enormous chests!

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: When I hang out with Kazuma, I get to eat lots of tasty stuff!

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: When I grow up, I'm gonna open my own meat shop! Then I can eat as much as I want!

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: Melissa is nice enough, but why is she always tryin' to rub my ears?

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: Who's my favorite member of Axel Hearts? Umm... I like them all!

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: Why do so many people visit the shop and just stare at me? C'mon, buy something already!

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: It's super fun being in Axel!

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: After all that hard work, I wanna reward, and by reward I mean delicious MEAT!

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: I'm the best veggie seller 'round!

name: Game Title 1
quote_text: God's Blessing on this Wonderful World! Fantastic Days

name: Game Title 2
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Game Title 3
quote_text: KonoSuba!

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: What's the ruckus? Is it someone's birthday? ...Oh, it's mine!

name: Amy 1 (Soother of Spirits)
quote_text: I'm always here for you, even when times are tough.

name: Amy 2 (Soother of Spirits)
quote_text: If there's anything I can do, just ask.

name: Amy 1 (Motherly Protector)
quote_text: I'll cook you up a scrumptious smorgasbord.

name: Amy 2 (Motherly Protector)
quote_text: Hehe. You're such a baby. I suppose that makes me your mother?

name: Amy 1 (Sage)
quote_text: I hope everyone feels right as rain!

name: Amy 2 (Sage)
quote_text: It's up to me to protect Mia. I wouldn't know what to do if she got hurt.

name: Amy 1 (Casual)
quote_text: Mia's the cutest thing alive.

name: Amy 2 (Casual)
quote_text: The place I'm from is unbelievably cold. So, this is a mite underdressed for me.

name: Amy 1 (Beginner)
quote_text: To us northern beastmen, farming is a way of life.

name: Amy 2 (Beginner)
quote_text: Since we ventured south, every day has been a blast for Mia.

name: Amy 1 (Motherly Maiden)
quote_text: Look at Mia giving her all! Isn't she the cutest?

name: Amy 2 (Motherly Maiden)
quote_text: Working as a maid and helping others is a splendid profession.

name: Amy 1 (Oasis Dancer)
quote_text: I'll be dancing at the next village festival. I hope you like it!

name: Amy 2 (Oasis Dancer)
quote_text: Cielo's a little scary, but she's a great dance instructor!

name: Amy 1 (Clean Your Plate)
quote_text: Let's do our best today, so make sure to clean your plate!

name: Amy 2 (Clean Your Plate)
quote_text: Tired? Here, let me feed you. Open wide!

name: Amy 1 (Cake Creator)
quote_text: Which cake do you like better, Mia? Mine or Kazuma's?

name: Amy 2 (Cake Creator)
quote_text: This is a special cake made from all of Mia's favorites. I hope she likes it.

name: Amy 1 (Me Time)
quote_text: Looks like she's fallen asleep. I hope your beauty sleep pays off!

name: Amy 2 (Me Time)
quote_text: If you have trouble sleeping, I'll sing you a lullaby.

name: Amy 1 (Relaxing Kunoichi)
quote_text: Sneaking around, fighting, taking baths... Being a kunoichi is hard work.

name: Amy 2 (Relaxing Kunoichi)
quote_text: I promised Mia I'd play ninja with her. She's so excited.

name: Amy 1 (Snow Country Starlight)
quote_text: Aren't the stars pretty tonight? I made us some hot cocoa so we can gaze at them outside.

name: Amy 2 (Snow Country Starlight)
quote_text: Mia's so cute when she's excited for the Harvest Festival. I can't wait for next year.

name: Amy 1 (Shy Swimmer)
quote_text: Um, Kazuma? It's a little embarrassing to have you looking at me like that...

name: Amy 2 (Shy Swimmer)
quote_text: This swimsuit feels a little small. What do you think?

name: Amy 1 (Blossoming Evening)
quote_text: The Crimson Demons sure are amazing, making such beautiful flowers bloom in the sky.

name: Amy 2 (Blossoming Evening)
quote_text: So this is a summer festival... It's quite different from the ones we have in Samuidoh.

name: Amy (Mama Pumpkin) 1
quote_text: I made lots of tasty treats. Let's all eat them together!

name: Amy (Mama Pumpkin) 2
quote_text: Isn't Mia so adorable in her costume? I'll give her a treat, but she's welcome to trick me too!

name: Amy (Nothing like a Hot Meal) 1
quote_text: Oops! Your nose is running... Here, let me wipe it for you.

name: Amy (Nothing like a Hot Meal) 2
quote_text: Are you cold? You're shivering. Here, warm yourself up with some hot soup!

name: Amy 1 (Sound of Wind)
quote_text: The sound of the landscape seems to bring cool air… It's great.

name: Amy 2 (Sound of Wind)
quote_text: Is the heat getting to you? Eat plenty and rest well.

name: Amy 1 (Keeper of Dream)
quote_text: Mia’s cute sleeping face… I can watch her all night…

name: Amy 2 (Keeper of Dream)
quote_text: The greatest gift for me… is Mia.

name: Amy 1 (Little Detective)
quote_text: Mia and Komekko are already best friends.

name: Amy 2 (Little Detective)
quote_text: After playing to your heart’s content, eat a lot, and stay healthy.

name: Amy (Smile of Angel) 1
quote_text: Don't push yourself too hard, okay? You can leave anything tough to me.

name: Amy (Smile of Angel) 2
quote_text: Can you eat apples? Here, say ahh~...

name: Assist
quote_text: If you'll have me, then gladly.

name: Assist
quote_text: Do you need help?

name: Claire 1 (Start)
quote_text: Symphonia Field Claire. I am the one with the duty to escort Princess Iris.

name: Claire 2 (Start)
quote_text: Kazuma Satou… How dare you influence Princess Iris in such a negative way?!

name: Claire 1 (The Escort of The Princess)
quote_text: With the glory of the house of Symphonia, I will protect Princess Iris.

name: Claire 2 (The Escort of The Princess)
quote_text: While I am away from the castle, Lain will escort Princess Iris.

name: Claire 1 (Outstanding Servant)
quote_text: Do I seem busy? It’s obvious since I’m carrying out my responsibilities as one of the leaders of this nation.

name: Claire 2 (Outstanding Servant)
quote_text: If you are rude to Princess Iris, consider your life gone.

name: Claire 1 (For The Princess)
quote_text: As long as I’m alive, you won't be able lay a finger on Princess Iris.

name: Claire 2 (For The Princess)
quote_text: The way Princess Iris looks… I want to record everything with the magic camera…!

name: Claire 1 (The Best Sukiyaki)
quote_text: Even if it is my day off, I can't believe I can’t stay by Princess Iris’ side… Ugh!

name: Claire 2 (The Best Sukiyaki)
quote_text: It's quite refreshing since I’ve never had the chance to gather ingredients with my own hands.

name: Claire (Knight's Summer Vacation) 1
quote_text: It doesn't feel so bad to feel the sea breeze without thinking about anything.

name: Claire (Knight's Summer Vacation) 2
quote_text: Lady Iris wearing her swimsuit is brighter than the sun and shinier than the ocean... S-So beautiful...!

name: Claire (Lady Iris, your Horn!) 1
quote_text: I-I'm sorry...! I-I can't believe something like this happened...!

name: Claire (Lady Iris, your Horn!) 2
quote_text: Ahhhh! Lady Iris! Y-Your precious horn...!

name: Claire (Holy Night's Knight) 1
quote_text: Lady Iris's beautiful smile is the greatest Christmas gift...!

name: Claire (Holy Night's Knight) 2
quote_text: Is this a custom from that guy's hometown...? Christmas... It's quite nice.

name: Vanir 1 (Beginner)
quote_text: I am the mind-reading devil, Vanir. Do not forget it.

name: Vanir 2 (Beginner)
quote_text: So many thoughts are dancing through your mind...I see them all.

name: Vanir 1 (Masked Demon)
quote_text: Demons are sticklers for contractual obligations, so feel free to trust me.

name: Vanir 2 (Masked Demon)
quote_text: I shall help you with challenging quests with lavish rewards... Haha! Just kidding!

name: Vanir 1 (Duke of Aprons)
quote_text: Welcome! That pitiful shopkeeper is away at the moment, so today is your lucky day.

name: Vanir 2 (Duke of Aprons)
quote_text: You've come to the right place! Good adventurers stock up on magic items before a quest!

name: Vanir 1 (Punishing Pose)
quote_text: Have you learned nothing, you pitiful shopkeeper?! I'll send you to oblivion with my Death Ray!

name: Vanir 2 (Punishing Pose)
quote_text: No sooner do we turn a profit than she blows it on junk. I can't turn my back on her for a second.

name: Vanir 1 (Duke of Hell)
quote_text: Mwahaha! Go forth, my dolls. It is time to cleanse the dungeon!

name: Vanir 2 (Duke of Hell)
quote_text: No, this dungeon won't do at all. When ever shall I strike upon the perfect dungeon?

name: Vanir 1 (Perfect Dungeon)
quote_text: Welcome to Vanir's Dungeon! Your fearless acceptance of my challenge is worthy of respect.

name: Vanir 2 (Perfect Dungeon)
quote_text: I see it! I can see it! You will spring a trap in the dungeon and run for your lives!

name: Vanir (Holy Night Profit) 1
quote_text: Line up and take advantage of our special Christmas sale!

name: Vanir (Holy Night Profit) 2
quote_text: Ahahaha! This holiday cheer might be enough to get us out of the red.

name: Vanir (New Year Predictions) 1
quote_text: May your year be full of happiness...and plenty of demons!

name: Vanir (New Year Predictions) 2
quote_text: A mask and Japanese clothing make for an odd but innovative pairing, no? How do I look?

name: Vanir (Card Sharp) 1
quote_text: Come now. I am Vanir, the mind-reading devil. I already know the outcome of your gambit.

name: Vanir (Card Sharp) 2
quote_text: Gambling is mere child's play for a demon like me.

name: Vanir 1 (Finale of Mask)
quote_text:
You don't have to refuse. It says it is
lucky to fall in love with the presence of me tonight.

name: Vanir 2 (Finale of Mask)
quote_text: Tragedies filled with unpleasantness are delightful comedies to me!

name: Vanir 1 (Relaxing Sunset)
quote_text: Blue sea! Beautiful sky! Add negativity to that and there's nothing more to wish for!

name: Vanir 2 (Relaxing Sunset)
quote_text: Limited open! Please come visit my beach store!

name: Vanir 1 (Welcome!)
quote_text: Welcome! Perfect timing. I've the perfect product for you.

name: Vanir 2 (Welcome!)
quote_text: You stupid shopkeeper! How many times do I have to tell you to understand!!

name: Vanir 1 (Legendary Archdemon)
quote_text: Muhaha... Hahaha! You may call me the Legendary Archdemon.

name: Vanir 2 (Legendary Archdemon)
quote_text: You were lucky enough to get this far, adventurer! …Hmm, will this be okay for the line?

name: Vanir (Unique Pose) 1
quote_text: Since they might be materials from an ideal dungeon, let’s play around with them and have some fun.

name: Vanir (Unique Pose) 2
quote_text: ...The energy that the comic race pours on being awesome or cool surprises me every time.

name: Assist
quote_text: Welcome to the gates of Hell, friend!

name: Assist
quote_text: Because I’m the goddess of fortune.

name: Assist
quote_text: M-M-M-Meow!!!

name: Emilia 1 (Spiritual Arts User)
quote_text: Spiritual arts users will leave you reeling if you don't watch out!

name: Emilia 2 (Spiritual Arts User)
quote_text: Even Puck was surprised by the Megumin's magic power!

name: Emilia 1 (Beach Volleyball)
quote_text: The swimsuit that Aqua made, it's so cute. I’m going to show it to Puck.

name: Emilia 2 (Beach Volleyball)
quote_text: Lugunica has giant lakes and rivers…

name: Rem 1 (Battle Maid)
quote_text: I will protect you.

name: Rem 2 (Battle Maid)
quote_text: Why does Lady Darkness like watching me hit things?

name: Rem 1 (With My Older Sister)
quote_text: I will prepare it so that you guys can relax on the beach.

name: Rem 2 (With My Older Sister)
quote_text: Rem is a bit embarrassed wearing something like this.

name: Mel 1 (Beginner)
quote_text: Lightning Spirit Mel, at your service! You can call me Mel for short.

name: Mel 2 (Beginner)
quote_text: Would you like to be my friend? I promise there'll never be a dull day when you're with me.

name: Mel 1 (Lightning Spirit)
quote_text: Zap! Heh, did I shock you? It's just a little thing I do when I meet people.

name: Mel 2 (Lightning Spirit)
quote_text: As my friend, you'll be privy to the exclusive reward of unlimited access to...being pranked, by me.

name: Mel 1 (Casual)
quote_text: Please don't tell Squall that I've been playing pranks again.

name: Mel 2 (Casual)
quote_text: Axel is very pleasant, and I have many friends here.

name: Mel 1 (Warm Welcome)
quote_text: Welcome to my home! I promise to treat you to some extra special pranks!

name: Mel 2 (Warm Welcome)
quote_text: I never thought I would be able to host friends at my house one day.

name: Mel 1 (Spirit Power)
quote_text: Anyone who tries to hurt my friends should know that a prank will be least of their worries!

name: Mel 2 (Spirit Power)
quote_text: You're about to feel the true power of a spirit... Lightning Bolt!

name: Mel 1 (Excuse Me)
quote_text: The prankster has been pranked... How could it come to this? I guess this is goodbye, friends!

name: Mel 2 (Excuse Me)
quote_text: That wasn't one of my better pranks, but I'll do better tomorrow, I promise!

name: Mel (Showtime) 1
quote_text: I'm not finished yet! I'll give you an electrifying performance!

name: Mel (Showtime) 2
quote_text: That prank had everyone in stitches! I think I might have to do it again!

name: Mel (Sweets of Joy) 1
quote_text: Mmm... How delicious! There's nothing like sharing scrumptious treats with friends!

name: Mel (Sweets of Joy) 2
quote_text: Back when I was sealed away, we never had festivals like this! How fun!

name: Mel (Unabashed) 1
quote_text: I was surprised to see Kazuma approve of my hot spring pranks.

name: Mel (Unabashed) 2
quote_text: Everyone lets their guard down in the hot springs... It's the perfect place to play some pranks!

name: Mel 1 (Lightning Service)
quote_text: Do come in! I've warmed up this electric bath for you!

name: Mel 2 (Lightning Service)
quote_text: A little prank while she's on service… What a good idea hehehe!

name: Mel 1 (Quest Reward)
quote_text: You can make more friends and earn more money if you take on lots of quests!

name: Mel 2 (Quest Reward)
quote_text: My adventure has only just begun…!

name: Mel 1 (Thrilling Race)
quote_text: I the Beach Lightning, will dominate this game!

name: Mel 2 (Thrilling Race)
quote_text: I'll take the flag of victory~!

name: Mel 1 (Dazzling Sunrise)
quote_text: Happy New Year! I’m going to pull a lot of pranks of you this year as well!

name: Mel 2 (Dazzling Sunrise)
quote_text: Although the sun is always there, it’s deeply moving to think that this is a brand new year.

name: Mel (Special Tingling Mochi) 1
quote_text: I'm so busy that I don't have any time to mess around... *Gasp*, we can hire a new staff-meow!

name: Mel (Special Tingling Mochi) 2
quote_text: Welco-meow! Cat Eared Shrine Maiden Tea House is open for business-meow!

name: Bell 1 (Little Rookie)
quote_text: It's my job to protect the Goddess... Fire Bolt!

name: Bell 2 (Little Rookie)
quote_text: Axel is such a tranquil town. I was pretty surprised by the flying vegetables though.

name: Ais 1 (Sword Princess)
quote_text: It doesn't matter if it's above ground or in a dungeon. I'll defeat every monster I face.

name: Ais 2 (Sword Princess)
quote_text: Darkness is so muscular, she'll be stronger in no time with the proper training.

name: Ainz (Supreme Undead King) 1
quote_text: Ainz Ooal Gown never loses. Never has. Never will.

name: Ainz (Supreme Undead King) 2
quote_text: (This will make for a crazy story when we get home to Nazarick.)

name: Ainz (Rare Item Aficionado) 1
quote_text: (This world is amazing! Just look at all these items!)

name: Ainz (Rare Item Aficionado) 2
quote_text: It's not just the items. The monsters here are equally fascinating.

name: Albedo (Guardian Overseer) 1
quote_text: O Lord Ainz, the Supreme One! Your magnificence spans the entire universe.

name: Albedo (Guardian Overseer) 2
quote_text: That slimy little eel... I see through her transparent attempts to get Lord Ainz alone.

name: Shalltear (Captivating Vampire) 1
quote_text: Megumin's introductions are so theatrical, but mimicking her was quite enjoyable.

name: Shalltear (Captivating Vampire) 2
quote_text: I've had enough of that over-sized gorilla. I should be the one by Lord Ainz's side.

name: Assist
quote_text: I'll handle this!

quote_text: Now, let's begin.

name: Battle 2
quote_text: Don't let your guard down.

name: Battle 3
quote_text: Stay on your toes.

name: Battle 4
quote_text: Mission complete.

name: Battle 5
quote_text: Let's return.

name: Battle 6
quote_text: Let's retreat for now.

name: Battle 7
quote_text: Haaah!

name: Battle 8
quote_text: Hmph!

name: Battle 9
quote_text: It's working.

name: Battle 10
quote_text: Shut up.

name: Battle 11
quote_text: Are you okay?

name: Battle 12
quote_text: Do you need help?

name: Battle 13
quote_text: We won't have to suffer...

name: Battle 14
quote_text: Ugh!

name: Battle 15
quote_text: Fighting isn't an objective.

name: Battle 16
quote_text: Preparation, complete.

name: Battle 17
quote_text: I'm fine.

name: Battle 18
quote_text: What are you doing?

name: Battle 19
quote_text: I was waiting for you.

name: Battle 1
quote_text: This is Beta, initiating mission.

name: Battle 2
quote_text: There is new enemy.

name: Battle 3
quote_text: I'm feeling great.

name: Battle 4
quote_text: Mission is completed.

name: Battle 5
quote_text: Raise it back again.

name: Battle 6
quote_text: No way…!

name: Battle 7
quote_text: Hyah!

name: Battle 8
quote_text: There!

name: Battle 9
quote_text: If you get in the way...!

name: Battle 10
quote_text: I will end this in an instant!

name: Battle 11
quote_text: I will support you!

name: Battle 12
quote_text: That's enough...

name: Battle 13
quote_text: I will show you the wisdom of the shadow!

name: Battle 14
quote_text: Ugh.

name: Battle 15
quote_text: I will retreat...!

name: Battle 16
quote_text: Preparation completed. Give me orders!

name: Battle 17
quote_text: Don't worry about it...!

name: Battle 18
quote_text: Am I on standby?

name: Battle 19
quote_text: I have the situation under control!

name: Amy 6 (Motherly Maiden)
quote_text: Why don't we take a short break?

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: You're an angel for inviting us into your party. Mia's been having the time of her life.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: It snows year-round up north. But that doesn't stop us from growing our famous greens.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: I'm hoping to sell off some produce today. The profits will buy Mia a hearty meal.

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: My, you seem tired. Here...rest your sweet head on my lap.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: That Mia's such a firecracker. She's so adorable.

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: What's that, darling? You want to touch my ears? ...Okay, just don't go overboard.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: What's wrong, sweetie? Did you have a bad dream?

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: Don't push yourself too hard, dearie. You're doing a wonderful job as is.

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: Now, now. Don't be naughty.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: Tee hee. Oh, you big baby... Whatever would you do without me, hm?

name: Greeting
quote_text: Can I interest you in some tasty veggies from the Northlands?

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: Now I'll be an even bigger help to the team.

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: Oh, my. Is it just me, or have I gotten stronger?

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: Will business pick up? I've got greens to sell.

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: Mia will be thrilled when she hears this.

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: Huh, I must be having a growth spurt.

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: You're too kind.

name: Battle 1
quote_text: Let's get started.

name: Battle 2
quote_text: Be a doll and fight by my side, hm?

name: Battle 3
quote_text: Tired, sweetie? Would a nap on my lap do the trick?

name: Battle 4
quote_text: You've done so much. Let Big Sis take the reins.

name: Battle 5
quote_text: It seems even your big sis has room to improve...

name: Battle 6
quote_text: Must...protect...Mia...

name: Battle 7
quote_text: This may hurt, but there's no need to cry.

name: Battle 8
quote_text: Take that!

name: Battle 9
quote_text: That's a no-no.

name: Battle 10
quote_text: Simmer down now.

name: Battle 11
quote_text: Very well done.

name: Battle 12
quote_text: Which of you deserves a reward?

name: Battle 13
quote_text: Big Sis will make it all better.

name: Battle 14
quote_text: Eek!

name: Battle 15
quote_text: I think I need a little sit-down.

name: Battle 16
quote_text: Tsk, tsk. Someone's been naughty.

name: Battle 17
quote_text: This calls for more veggies.

name: Battle 18
quote_text: I'm sure I can be of help.

name: Battle 19
quote_text: Big Sis will give it all she's got, okay?

name: Battle 20
quote_text: Let's give this our best!

name: Battle 21
quote_text: Mia, are you all right?

name: Battle 22
quote_text: Great work!

name: Battle 23
quote_text: I couldn't have done this without your help.

name: Battle 24
quote_text: There's always next time.

name: Battle 25
quote_text: I can't move a muscle...

name: Battle 26
quote_text: All right!

name: Battle 27
quote_text: Hey!

name: Battle 28
quote_text: That might have hurt a little too much.

name: Battle 29
quote_text: Nice job!

name: Battle 30
quote_text: There, there.

name: Battle 31
quote_text: Be good now.

name: Battle 32
quote_text: Pain, pain, go away!

name: Battle 33
quote_text: Huh?!

name: Battle 34
quote_text: This is only a temporary withdrawal.

name: Battle 35
quote_text: Somebody deserves a pat on the head.

name: Battle 36
quote_text: I feel so tired...

name: Battle 37
quote_text: What's wrong? You want to be spoiled?

name: Battle 38
quote_text: If you win, I'll give you a big hug.

name: Misc 1
quote_text: Hehe. Such a kind soul.

name: Misc 2
quote_text: It's been ages since someone took care of me for a change.

name: Misc 3
quote_text: Nothing beats beastmen veggies, we always say.

name: Misc 4
quote_text: Mia is like a little sister to me.

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Oh, I think that's quite enough excitement for one day. Relax, you'll thank me later.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: Mia's just the cutest thing ever! The very light of my life.

name: Misc 7
quote_text: Come to me anytime, my sweet.

name: Misc 8
quote_text: Hehehe... Feeling tired, Melissa? Want some fluffy time?

name: Misc 9
quote_text: If you're ever in trouble, you can count on me.

name: Misc 10
quote_text: Wiz is very nurturing. I think she'll make a great mom.

name: Misc 11
quote_text: We had a lot of sales today. I'll close up and get supper started.

name: Misc 12
quote_text: I like taking care of people, so don't worry about it.

name: Misc 13
quote_text: Cielo punched another guy? I like her style!

name: Misc 14
quote_text: Lia's room is a total mess again. I guess I'll have to clean it for her.

name: Misc 15
quote_text: I wish I could feed Mia her favorite foods every day.

name: Misc 16
quote_text: Ah! T'was down right amazin'! Ahem, sorry. My accent flared up again.

name: Misc 17
quote_text: I'm glad you made friends with Mia. Thanks, Yunyun.

name: Misc 18
quote_text: Way to go, Megumin! Another nice explosion today!

name: Misc 19
quote_text: Mia bought me some food, but it's too precious to eat.

name: Misc 20
quote_text: I never feel it is a burden to help someone in need.

name: Misc 21
quote_text: Feeling tired? In need of pampering? Come and lay your head on my lap.

name: Misc 22
quote_text: Kazuma is like a big brother to Mia.

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: Mia is the cutest thing in the world. Just look at her!

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: Are you tired? Feel free to rest your weary head on my lap if you like.

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: There's nothing my healing magic and beastman veggies can't cure.

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: Oh dear, you shouldn't be so finicky.

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: If you're not getting enough sleep, I'm good at singing lullabies.

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: I have Kazuma to thank for selling so many veggies. He's a real help.

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: Mia is so cute when she pretends to be a member of Axel Hearts.

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: I hope Mia experiences the kind of friendship that Lia and the other girls have someday.

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: Am I tired? Hehe, I'm fine. Thank you for your concern, though.

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: I'm so glad Mia's had such a wonderful time since we opened our shop here in Axel.

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: It's nice to pat yourself on the back once in a while. I think I did a pretty good job.

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: Hm? It looks like my chest might have gotten bigger again...

name: Greeting
quote_text: Symphonia Field Claire. Protecting Princess Iris is my duty!

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: Princess Iris will personally thank the one who performed exceptionally well.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: Kazuma’s bad influence can’t be overlooked... But he doesn’t seem like a bad person.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: Why does Lady Aqua accompany a man like that when she has that much power?

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: With Megumin's firepower backed by the Kingdom army, they might be able to overthrow the Devil King’s army.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: Dame Dustiness, thank you for always leading the way.

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: I heard there was a shop in Axel that sells amazing items. Will it help our nation increase it’s forces?

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: That man is so great with tricks. I can't help but acknowledge his wit.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: If it's to protect Princess Iris, I will not hesitate to lay down my life.

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: I can't believe I received a gift from Princess Iris…! I have to keep it under lock and key!

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: Take a bath with Princess Iris…? It could never happen, what are you saying?!

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: I just want to be of some help to Princess Iris.

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: Princess Iris is essential for the future of this nation.

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: Axel town? From a masked gentleman to a lightning spirit, and beastmen… Many unique people are gathered here.

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: You’ve received an invitation from Princess Iris? Then you are our guests for tonight, please enjoy.

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: Princess Iris smiled at me… Ugh, I’m getting nauseous from joy!

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: I hope you would lend us this strength to slay the Demon King.

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: This town is always so peaceful no matter when I visit.

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: I hope the day Princess Iris can lay down her sword someday.

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: Princess Iris has been speaking very informally… Is it that man again?

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: Princess Iris is the greatest swordsman.

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: This power… I will use it for this nation, for Princess Iris.

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: Let’s triumph with our honed skills.

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: I'll try to be of help.

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: As an escort, as a swordsman, I will continue to strive for power.

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: It’s my duty to hone my skills and protect my lord!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: The house of Symphonia is as famous as the house of Dustiness.

name: Misc 2
quote_text: It's great to have reliable allies.

name: Misc 3
quote_text: I prefer paying back my debts. I will lend you my strength if something happens.

name: Misc 4
quote_text: I will do anything if it’s Princess Iris’ commands!

name: Misc 5
quote_text: I am deeply moved my Princess Iris’ gentleness.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: You, did you influence Princess Iris in a bad way again?!

name: Misc 7
quote_text: Princess Iris! Please don't call that man your brother!

name: Misc 8
quote_text: Nobles have a responsibility to lead and defend the people.

name: Misc 9
quote_text: No, ma’am! If you do that… P-Princess Iris?!

name: Misc 10
quote_text: You want to know about Princess Iris’ charms? That will cost you two days of your time.

name: Misc 11
quote_text: T-There is no way that I would call Princess Iris, “Cute”!

name: Misc 12
quote_text: Don’t mistake it, The generous Princess Iris is only working together to help you guys.

name: Misc 13
quote_text: Don't listen to his story! This man… is hopeless!

name: Misc 14
quote_text: Fried frogs? There is no way such commoner’s food will satisfy Princess Iris’ taste buds…

name: Misc 15
quote_text: Hmm… even if commoner's food, it doesn't taste so bad.

name: Misc 16
quote_text: Princess Iris expresses her gratitude for your performances.

name: Misc 17
quote_text: Thank you for coming. Please enjoy the hospitality of the royal capital today.

name: Misc 18
quote_text: I will cut down anyone who harms Princess Iris with my sword.

name: Misc 19
quote_text: Princess Iris! Please do not speak with that man too much. His stupidity might be contagious.

name: Misc 20
quote_text: You probably never experienced such a fancy feast, right? Make sure to thank Princess Iris.

name: Misc 21
quote_text: Princess Iris! What is the meaning of this ruckus this time?!

name: Misc 22
quote_text: Work hard for Princess Iris. If you do well, I will consider a long residence within the castle.

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: It looks like the Trial of the Ancients have been unlocked.

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: Let’s advance. Make sure not to let your guard down.

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: Leave the battle to me.

name: Greeting
quote_text: I am the mind-reading devil Vanir, perhaps even stronger than the Devil King himself!

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: I am Vanir! Duke of Hell and former Devil King Army Commander himself! Well met.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: Your agony tastes absolutely sublime!

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: Shall I take over your body? Mwahahaha!

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: Save feasting on negative emotions, I pride myself on being forthright with everyone.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: Demons are sticklers for contractual obligations, so feel free to trust me.

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: You seriously thought you could deceive me? A mind-reading devil is not easily fooled.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: There is no greater delicacy than crippling disappointment in the face of failure.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: If I must die, let it be while devouring the sweetest suffering that can be found!

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: One has nothing to lose doing business with me! The deal will be win-win for the both of us!

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: Well well... I did not see you surviving this far. Impressive.

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: I'll have you know children find my mask very cool. I smell a business opportunity!

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: The pitiful shopkeeper here is an old friend. *Sigh* I just wish she wasn't so incompetent.

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: Despite being so young, you know much that I do not. I find it very intriguing.

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: I see you are infatuated with everything about me. Oh how I shall revel in disappointing you!

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: What is this...happiness I sense? I am not finding it very pleasant at all.

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: You find me in a good mood. Come, let me read your fortune before I change my mind.

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: Why do I cooperate with one such as you? Why, for personal gain, of course.

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: If there is something in it for me, I'll do just about anything.

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: That horrid goddess causes such a ruckus at the shop... She's practically a demon herself.

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: I have lived for many eons, but yes... I find this to be rather interesting.

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: Ah... I sense the potential for something greater.

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: I see! I see!

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: What did you say?!

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: What's this now?

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: I wish the shop's sales were this successful...

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: Mwahahaha! There are no limits when you are eternal!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: Mwahahaha! Such exquisite agony!

name: Misc 2
quote_text: To a demon, there is nothing more delicious than human despair.

name: Misc 3
quote_text: I have no choice but to take control of the shop from that pitiful shopkeeper!

name: Misc 4
quote_text: Nobody in this town is more industrious than me.

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Why can't I see the future of that worthless shopkeeper?

name: Misc 6
quote_text: Welcome! Peruse our fine wares at your leisure!

name: Misc 7
quote_text: You find my sales techniques shady? Many a housewife would disagree!

name: Misc 8
quote_text: It's garbage day tomorrow. I'll need to drive off those crows before they make a mess.

name: Misc 9
quote_text: Alas, it is I!

name: Misc 10
quote_text: Having a body made of mere earth means I can make another whenever I desire.

name: Misc 11
quote_text: I will never get used to that walking disaster of a goddess.

name: Misc 12
quote_text: The boy's nose for money is admirable—almost as much as my ability to swerve it.

name: Misc 13
quote_text: That pigheaded crusader is an enigma to me, but I find her spirit commendable.

name: Misc 14
quote_text: Let us see which is more powerful: your explosion magic or my Death Ray.

name: Misc 15
quote_text: I foresaw the moment you would dance before me! Excellent!

name: Misc 16
quote_text: Hmm... You are a dancer who fears men? As a demon, my true form is without gender.

name: Misc 17
quote_text: Divining is not needed to know that adventurer will meet an untimely end.

name: Misc 18
quote_text: I have a strict policy against killing humans... Note that I only said humans, though!

name: Misc 19
quote_text: Merely mentioning "friendship" despirits that Crimson Demon girl. How delish!

name: Misc 20
quote_text: Remember, all sales are final. Read the manual before you buy anything.

name: Misc 21
quote_text: The apron is a staple of our shop uniform, picked out by yours truly.

name: Misc 22
quote_text: My real body is this mask... H-Hey, stop trying to pull it off!

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: Mwahahaha! This is but a fraction of my power!

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: My power is already unmatched. The world would shake if I gained more.

name: Greeting
quote_text: I am Emilia, candidate for the throne of the Kingdom of Lugunica.

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: You shouldn't get involved with me.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: I'm a half-elf... Doesn't that frighten you?

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: Why do you insist on helping me?

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: Thank you, but don't overdo it, all right?

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: I've never been so happy in all my life.

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: Do you want to study together? I can teach you how to read and write.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: Puck is like a parent to me...or something like that.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: The moon is beautiful tonight! Tomorrow will be a good day.

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: Put your head in my lap, just this once.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: Thank you, as always. Let me know if I can help you, too.

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: Puck calls me Lia, just like the dancer in this world!

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: Chomusuke and Puck sure get along well!

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: Light of Saber is one awesome spell! Do you think I can learn it?

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: The goddess Eris has silver hair too. It's nice to have something in common.

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: Axel is such a lively town! I really like it here.

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: I feel stronger than ever!

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: I must become stronger.

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: This warmth is cozy.

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: This is what I've trained for!

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: Thank you sooo much!

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: I've come this far thanks to your help.

name: Misc 1
quote_text: Ugh, Subaru is such a dolt!

name: Misc 2
quote_text: Hehe! Thank you. I'm really happy.

name: Misc 3
quote_text: I want to help everyone I can.

name: Misc 4
quote_text: Thanks for choosing me.

name: Misc 5
quote_text: I love Puck and Puck loves me.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: Subaru's always overdoing it. He's beyond help.

name: Misc 7
quote_text: Rewards only go to those who earn them—that's why they're rewards!

name: Greeting
quote_text: I am Rem, a servant of Lord Roswaal.

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: My name is Rem. My homemaking skills are at your service.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: How terrible. You are being violated in our guest's mind.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: This uniform is enough for me. I have no need for other clothes.

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: My sister has a much kinder soul.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: Hard work is good for the heart.

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: Few things are as elegant as my sister's vegetable peeling.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: Don't forget your promise.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: Impressive. Just as I expected!

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: Who do I like? Hehe... I won't tell.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: Wherever Subaru goes, he'll always have a demon with him!

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: Do you have mayonnaise? I want to give some to Subaru.

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: All you need to cook...is a cooking skill? That's amazing.

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: Aqua is so talented. Was she a performer?

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: Do you think Subaru would be happy if I called him dearest brother?

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: Are you tired from questing? If you're ok with it, you can use my lap as a pillow.

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: I can feel energy rushing through me!

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: Let us start here, from square one.

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: Do you think I'm a little stronger?

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: I'm all warmed up!

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: Fanatical like a demon!

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: Such strength is wasted on me.

name: Misc 1
quote_text: Teach you how to cook? Be prepared, I'm quite strict.

name: Misc 2
quote_text: Don't be afraid. I'm with you.

name: Misc 3
quote_text: I don't know if I can help, but I'll do my best!

name: Misc 4
quote_text: Sure, if it will help Subaru!

name: Misc 5
quote_text: My housekeeping skills are at your service.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: Subaru is a wonderful person.

name: Misc 7
quote_text: Please treat my sister and me well.

name: Greeting
quote_text: You there! Would you be my friend?! Please!

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: I'd very much like it if we became friends. We could pull pranks on people every day!

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: Lightning Bolt! Hehehe, did I shock you?

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: It's in my nature to be a nuisance. I couldn't change no matter how hard I tried.

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: Kazuma is my pranking master. He's taught me so much.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: Let's go on a quest! I'll scorch the hide off any monsters with my lightning strikes!

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: I want to find some friends in this world, but I do hope they'll be kinda cute.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: What fun shall we get up to today? Mischief? Tomfoolery? Or perhaps just plain pranking?

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: I'm meeting up with Yunyun! We're going to play some board games together.

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: Megumin marked me as a lightning-wielding rival. And here I thought we were friends...

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: Hello? Does anyone fancy being pranked? No...? I see...

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: I hope our friendship lasts for eternity.

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: Aqua can turn any drink into pure water! Just think of her pranking potential!

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: Lia is helping with my singing rehearsals. We're having an awfully good time!

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: The best pranks bring a smile to the faces of those being pranked. Amazing, isn't it?

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: I want to invite you to my house for some delicious tea cakes and boiling pepper-laced drinks.

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: Don't be shy, why don't you try some of this...delicious food I prepared for you. Hehehe...

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: I didn't like it when I was sealed away. All alone, with no one to talk to...

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: If I joined the Order of Axis, I'd have more friends than ever before! Where do I sign up?

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: I've prepared a song for children. Would you like to hear it?

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: If there's anything I might do to help, please let me know. We're friends, after all.

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: Such power!

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: I have the perfect prank!

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: My lightning has gotten stronger!

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: I hope this pleases my friends...

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: Oh my... I simply must put this power to use!

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: Now I can make as many friends as I like!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: Care to plan some new pranks with me?

name: Misc 2
quote_text: I got a job at the cafe that serves Samuidoh veggies. Stop by one day.

name: Misc 3
quote_text: I adventure with my friends every chance I get!

name: Misc 4
quote_text: Everyone's share of the loot is decided before venturing out. That's common knowledge among adventurers!

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Why would someone actively avoid making friends... I just don't understand.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: Kazuma was very mad at me, even though I didn't do anything wrong...

name: Misc 7
quote_text: You can make friends AND earn money—jobs have some upsides!

name: Misc 8
quote_text: Spend the day with me—you'll be surprised by how many pranks we can get up to!

name: Misc 9
quote_text: You may not remember this, but I am a lightning spirit, you know?

name: Misc 10
quote_text: I've grown very fond of singing lately. I hope I get a chance to perform again.

name: Misc 11
quote_text: One of the building blocks of pranking is making drinks spicy hot or very bitter.

name: Misc 12
quote_text: Mia laughs at all of my pranks... It warms my heart.

name: Misc 13
quote_text: Stubborn adults are prime targets for my punishing pranks!

name: Misc 14
quote_text: With power like mine, you could make a lightning-infused sword, no problem!

name: Misc 15
quote_text: Lia and the other girls are wonderful singers... I need to rehearse more...

name: Misc 16
quote_text: Friends don't hurt friends. Simple to say, difficult to achieve...

name: Misc 17
quote_text: It's good to shake someone's hand when you're making up with them. Or so I'm told!

name: Misc 18
quote_text: I don't remember much from when they say I had horns...

name: Misc 19
quote_text: I get withdrawal symptoms when I haven't pranked anyone in a while...

name: Misc 20
quote_text: Are you tired? How about I give you electric shock treatm—err, a massage?

name: Misc 21
quote_text: I have nothing but gratitude for whoever cast the explosion magic that freed me.

name: Misc 22
quote_text: If you ever feel like eating some lightning, I'd be happy to help.

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: My mischief grows ever stronger!

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: I'll use this power to protect my friends!

name: Greeting
quote_text: Bell Cranel, at your service!

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: Grandpa was right—the dungeon is pretty cool.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: The Goddess has saved me more times than I can remember. I need to shape up.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: That Kazuma is amazing. He could have his own Familia if he wanted.

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: So, what kind of heroes does this world have?

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: If you find yourself in trouble, I'm your guy.

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: I bet it would be fun being in your Familia, with Lady Aqua in charge.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: Shall we test our skills with a quest? You'll be shocked when you see how much I've grown.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: Vegetables can fly in your world? This is a strange place...

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: There are gods and goddesses in this world too? I'd very much like to meet one.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: I can't afford to waste a single second. I must train to become stronger.

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: Ais was kind enough to train me. I hope I didn't come across as a total novice...

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: Lili told me to "pull myself together" already. She's not wrong...

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: I'll take on any monster that stands in our way. But, I'm not that good with minotaurs.

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: I've read about the great heroes of yesteryear... I hope to become like them one day.

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: I'd be honored if you'd join our Familia. The Goddess would welcome you with open arms!

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: I leveled up, Goddess!

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: I must keep training until I'm much stronger.

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: I wish Ais were here to see me fight...

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: I'll do everything in my power to protect you all!

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: One step closer to reaching my goal.

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: It's... It's like I'm a new man!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: Thank you for everything you do!

name: Misc 2
quote_text: I promise to get stronger and return the favor!

name: Misc 3
quote_text: I don't know how much I can help, but I'll try my best!

name: Misc 4
quote_text: I've been waiting for a chance to show off my skill!

name: Misc 5
quote_text: I wonder if the Goddess is working today.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: Maybe Ais is free to train with me again...

name: Misc 7
quote_text: My grandpa always said that a good man needs a proper bevy of beauties.

name: Greeting
quote_text: If you ever need a monster dealt with, I'm the one to ask.

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: My name is Ais Wallenstein, but you can call me Ais if you want.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: I'm pretty good at teaching swordsmanship, but not much else.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: This world is really something. Compared to all the worlds I've seen, it's so peaceful.

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: Why can't I ever decide on what to do when I'm not on a quest or training?

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: Little Rookie really is the perfect nickname for Bell.

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: ...Did you hear that? It sounded like a monster.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: I will get stronger, and then I'll overcome the weakness within me.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: Kazuma has an interesting fighting style—very inventive. He reminds me of Bell, in a way.

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: That Darkness sure can take a hit.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: So Axel doesn't have a fried cheesy potato vendor anywhere, huh?

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: My specialty is Ariel magic—I control the wind, basically.

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: Every time I offer my lap to Bell as a pillow, he bolts away. What's a girl supposed to do?

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: The best way to eat fried cheesy potatoes is to be generous with the cream.

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: The wind of this world feels nice, but it's just not the same as the wind back home...

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: It is important that we don't let a single monster get away.

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: This is the fruit of my constant training.

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: I need to continue leveling up.

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: I guess I have the blessing of the gods to thank.

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: I can take on even more monsters now.

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: It's all about facing your fears.

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: I feel like I might have just become stronger.

name: Misc 1
quote_text: What kind of things do you like?

name: Misc 2
quote_text: Would you like to train together?

name: Misc 3
quote_text: I'm ready to take on the dungeon anytime.

name: Misc 4
quote_text: ...My nap training? It's all finished.

name: Misc 5
quote_text: I've gotten good at biding my time. It's the only way to deal with some monsters.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: I wonder if Bell is off fighting monsters right now.

name: Misc 7
quote_text: The way the wind blows here is wonderful.

name: Greeting
quote_text: I am Ainz Ooal Gown, but you may know me as the Supreme One of the Great Tomb of Nazarick.

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: I need to sort through all the magic items I'll be taking back to Nazarick with me.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: I may have no need for food, but that doesn't mean I can't share a table with friends.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: Feel free to show me any rare items you might have. I have coin to spare.

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: I see Hamsuke has adapted to this world without any issue.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: (Kazuma's a weird one. With loyal friends like his though, I wouldn't want to have to fight him.)

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: I hear she's a crusader, but I sometimes worry about Darkness's...enthusiasm.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: I hope one day to meet this mighty clan called the Crimson Demons in battle.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: She can be a bit reckless at times, but Shalltear's grit and determination often prove invaluable.

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: Explosion magic...? I must admit such power is beyond my current understanding.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: (If Aura and Mare were here, they would have a blast...)

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: It is thanks to my top lieutenant, Albedo, that I am able to move so freely.

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: I feel Aqua's disdain for me, but can't our disagreement be solved with words?

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: Anything can happen. I must save my super-tier magic for true emergencies.

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: I do hope Sebas and the others are handling things well in my absence.

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: (It'd be nice to have Kazuma and the others in Nazarick...as thanks for all they've done.)

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: Kneel before me...

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: (This takes me back... I remember my days of grinding to higher levels.)

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: One's skill level is synonymous with their power. Power up as much as you can.

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: (This is like I'm about to increase my skill level.)

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: Whoever said I've reached my limits?

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: (I hope I'm strong enough to match my title as Overlord.)

name: Misc 1
quote_text: They're being emotional. No need to worry, just give them time to cool off.

name: Misc 2
quote_text: Would you mind if I show you my collection of rare items?

name: Misc 3
quote_text: We must push forward. I have much to learn of this world.

name: Misc 4
quote_text: (I need to calm any fears they might have, given how I look...)

name: Misc 5
quote_text: I was warned of venturing into Arcanretia, but what lies there?

name: Misc 6
quote_text: Bizarre monsters, strange customs—it will take time to learn this world's mysteries.

name: Misc 7
quote_text: (Keeping quirky party members in line is hard in any world, I guess.)

name: Greeting
quote_text: I am Albedo, Guardian Overseer of the Great Tomb of Nazarick and legal wife of Lord Ainz.

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: I see Lord Ainz is able to swiftly enlist supporters in this or any other world.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: I live to serve His Lordship...in all manner of ways.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: As Guardian Overseer, I must ensure my judgments are free of flaw or fault.

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: Stuffing one's bosom into such a suffocating enclosure seems so...cruel.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: I can't believe Lord Ainz is so fond of that Kazuma Satou!

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: My lord is adored by one and all, but no one can compare to my love for him.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: The other guardians intrude on my quality time with Lord Ainz.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: They may be boisterous, but the Crimson Demons are not to be underestimated.

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: The guardians in charge of Nazarick were never meant to hold it forever.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: Darkness... She is an infinitely stubborn human. The likes of which I have never met.

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: More in this world should know the greatness of Lord Ainz.

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: *Sigh* I miss the pillow I made in honor of Lord Ainz...

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: The blue-haired shrew who would dare defy Lord Ainz deserves everything coming to her!

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: Ainz Ooal Gown... Be free, my lord...

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: That's one more outfit that Lord Ainz's and my child will have to wear!

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: Were you expecting another outcome?

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: I must not bring shame to the title of Guardian Overseer.

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: I hope Lord Ainz will be pleased.

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: I'm sure you are capable of more than this.

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: My feelings for Lord Ainz know no bounds.

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: I'm starting to feel a bit hot.

name: Misc 1
quote_text: Let me regale you with tales of Lord Ainz's brilliance.

name: Misc 2
quote_text: Join me, and we will serve Lord Ainz together.

name: Misc 3
quote_text: Have you seen Lord Ainz?

name: Misc 4
quote_text: I am happy to help, if His Lordship permits me.

name: Misc 5
quote_text: I wonder if Lord Ainz will ever see me as I see him...

name: Misc 6
quote_text: Just imagining the majesty of Lord Ainz overwhelms me utterly! Lord Ainz!

name: Misc 7
quote_text: Just Lord Ainz and me, alone in a strange, new world... Hehehe. Oh, I must behave.

name: Greeting
quote_text: I'm Shalltear, a cute little cold-blooded, cold-hearted, and cruel monster.

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: What's my job? Kicking annoying little stones out of Lord Ainz's path.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: Lord Ainz is our—no, all immortals'—master and ruler.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: *Sigh* There I go again, causing problems for Lord Ainz. Why do I do this?

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: Doesn't that loud-mouthed gorilla get tired of acting like that all the time?

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: How dare that Kazuma Satou speak to Lord Ainz so informally!

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: No guardian of the Great Tomb of Nazarick can ever match my skill.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: Oh how I admire Lord Ainz. He truly is a ruler of infinite mercy.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: It's tiring spending time with Megumin; she's obsessed with her intros and poses.

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: The blood of others is my strength. Pray you never meet me after I've fed.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: That Darkness... Why would a human wish to put herself in harm's way?

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: Just what kind of monster are these flying vegetables anyway?

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: I want to meet a human worthy of turning...

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: If I see that hot-blooded, blue-haired, self-righteous woman again, she's dead meat!

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: Einherjars are my trump card... One I'd dare not use if I'm being honest.

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: Perhaps it's time we built a new home in this world for Lord Ainz.

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: My strength exists to serve you, Lord Ainz!

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: I'm bursting with power.

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: You've just met perfection.

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: Lord Ainz will reward me for this.

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: You have yet to see my true power.

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: I must look my best for Lord Ainz!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: I will reward you by making you one of me.

name: Misc 2
quote_text: You would pledge your loyalty to me? Perhaps you are not so bad after all.

name: Misc 3
quote_text: If you need my help that badly, fine; I'll lend you my aid.

name: Misc 4
quote_text: Who would like to torn limb from limb next?

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Flying vegetables and fields of fish... This place is quite strange.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: The only help Lord Ainz needs in this world is mine.

name: Misc 7
quote_text: I'm low on blood. Are there any humans in the vicinity?

name: Greeting
quote_text: My name is Funifura! The best sibling-lover of the Crimson Demon... And!

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: If you're a Crimson Demon, you should introduce yourself properly, Dodonko.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: Huh? Before He was born.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: This is so unfair...! I heard that Megumin is the most famous Crimson Demon in Axel!

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: She is so stubborn.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: Wait, Dodonko! Don't you miss something before we go on the quest?

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: I understand. This is the shock I felt after a long time since I first saw Chomusuke.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: They say your wish comes true if you enter the Order of Axis, I wonder if it’s true.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: ...Isn't it the same pose you always make?

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: Megumin forgets our names sometimes.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: Wait! Y-You just tried to flirt with my younger sibling, right…?!

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: The magic that works best is “Light of Saber.”

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: Don’t just fall asleep all of a sudden like that.

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: Darkness is incredible, she knowingly goes to get attacked.

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: Yeah, yeah! what happened was, he grew 1mm!

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: Does Meguming have an ideal type... No, is there a lover from her past life?

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: No. I think it’s too early.

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: Have you find your destiny, Dodonko?

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: Let's farm it. Ask Yunyun to make it moderately weak.

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: I want a familiar spirit.

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: As expected, He’s one of “Vanir Milde” of the Crimson Demon Village.

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: I’m going to report to my brother!

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: I’ll crank up the efficiency.

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: There is no limit to my powers!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: All I need is my brother!

name: Misc 3
quote_text: Please take care of Dodonko as well.

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Great, is this enough for this month’s gift?

name: Misc 6
quote_text: You always say that, but you never remember it…

name: Misc 7
quote_text: When we borrowed money from Yunyun, Megumin was scary.

name: Misc 8
quote_text: What about it? I prepared measures so that he doesn’t get too close.

name: Misc 9
quote_text: No, this is a prototype from my shop. Do you want to try it?

name: Misc 10
quote_text: You're the one to talk, you’ve grown a lot in so many ways.

name: Misc 11
quote_text: *Yawn*… Lack of sleep is more an enemy to your skin than the gargoyle…

name: Misc 12
quote_text: That’s so inefficient, how did she get more skill points?

name: Misc 13
quote_text: I also want a nickname like the Crow Slayer..

name: Misc 14
quote_text: Oh, he still has a long way to go to becoming the principal like this.

name: Misc 15
quote_text: Excuse me, did you see Arue’s new piece this week?!

name: Misc 16
quote_text: Dodonko... You were also possessed by a demon called drowsiness!

name: Misc 17
quote_text: Wow, what's with that pile of pamphlets?

name: Misc 18
quote_text: You always take your pillow.

name: Misc 19
quote_text: Treasure Hunter… Should I aim for the jackpot for my brother?

name: Misc 20
quote_text: Hmph, it derived from her love for her brother from the previous life.. That’s it.

name: Misc 21
quote_text: I wonder if there is a great way to get noticed in the Axel Town!

name: Misc 22
quote_text: That’s won't happen because I’ve already made sure of it.

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: When looking down deep inside my heart, my brother is there…!

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: I’m close to becoming a brilliant mage!

name: Greeting
quote_text: My name is Dodonko! The best... Crimson... Ehh... What was it?

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: Aww, I forgot because I was taken aback, Funifura.

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: Hey, when did you start liking your brother, Funifura?

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: We also want to make our names known…!

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: I heard Megumin still don't call Yunyun a friend.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: ...On the top of that, where are we going?

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: I keep giving Mia, the beastman, food without realizing it.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: Then I should make a wish to stay asleep for the rest of my life.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: Hey, what do you think about this pose? Isn’t it awesome?

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: I wish she’d cut it out!

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: I might want a little sibling.

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: Yeah, I understand, it’s so awesome.

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: I’m feeling sleepy… Snore…

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: Is that displaying crisis? We should learn it too.

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: Huh? Funifura looks happy… Did something happen to her younger brother?

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: That’s what I was curious about too! But it’s still Megumin.

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: Excuse me, please cut that out and introduce me properly to your younger brother.

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: But you haven't found the lover from the past life either, Funifura.

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: Mmm, It's not easy to level up just by catching wild monsters.

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: Right, I like fluff ones like Chomusuke.

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: Could “Vanir” from the item shop be…?

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: I grew again.

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: I want to learn powerful magic.

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: I will become a elite Crimson Demon!

name: Misc 2
quote_text: I get sleepy when I’m relieved.

name: Misc 4
quote_text: Funifura is quite capable as well.

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Wow, you're sending all of that to your brother?!

name: Misc 6
quote_text: My name is Dodonko... Wait, it’s on the tip of my tongue!

name: Misc 7
quote_text: Yeah, her eyes were red.

name: Misc 8
quote_text: It looks like your brother likes Axel Hearts… Is that okay?

name: Misc 9
quote_text: Oh, did you get a new staff, Funifura?

name: Misc 10
quote_text: Wiz is incredible. She's an adult with great style.

name: Misc 11
quote_text: Really? I’ve never thought about it because I could fall asleep anywhere in less than two minutes.

name: Misc 12
quote_text: Yunyun leveled up really quickly. Is it because she’s a loner and practiced by herself?

name: Misc 13
quote_text: Funifura already has something called the “Brother Complex.”

name: Misc 14
quote_text: Teacher Pucchin must be in charge of new students again this year.

name: Misc 15
quote_text: I saw it! It was so great that I wanted everyone to see it.

name: Misc 16
quote_text: Ugh, at this rate… the empty space in my consciousness…!

name: Misc 17
quote_text: Some blonde girl handed it to me when I was walking around the street earlier…

name: Misc 18
quote_text: Funifura always takes a magic picture of her brother on quests.

name: Misc 19
quote_text: That’s the dream. I want to make a lot of money and just sleep all day.

name: Misc 20
quote_text: Come to think of it, how did Funifura get such a severe brother complex again?

name: Misc 21
quote_text: I can't let Megumin hog the spot as the representing Crimson Demon of the Axel Town.

name: Misc 22
quote_text: Hey, if your future brother gets a girlfriend…

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: Yeah, We might be going through her growing phase.

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: I get tired after working hard.

name: Greeting
quote_text: Call me Lolisa. My true identity is a secret.

name: Affinity 1
quote_text: Why are you looking at me like that? Are you attracted to me?

name: Affinity 2
quote_text: Thank you! Please write down your favorite dream in the survey.

name: Affinity 3
quote_text: Failed work… Ugh, please don't remind me of it.

name: Affinity 4
quote_text: We succubi live off fees and the vitality of men.

name: Affinity 5
quote_text: What do you mean like an actress… It wasn't that good. Hehe.

name: Affinity 6
quote_text: Who or whatever you are, you can do anything in your dreams.

name: Affinity 7
quote_text: I'd like to find a dugeon that Vanir would like.

name: Affinity 8
quote_text: So, that thing called shame… It's important?

name: Affinity 9
quote_text: I occasionally spend time with Yunyun.

name: Affinity 10
quote_text: I was told to be more confident…

name: Affinity 11
quote_text: Vanir can be so cruel! But that's also what makes him so great!

name: Affinity 12
quote_text: What a temper… Dust must be a devil right?

name: Affinity 13
quote_text: I'm tired of pitiful shoulder patting!

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: If only my Charm could work on Vanir… But that's impossible…

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: This is a free ticket. Please come visit if you can.

name: Affinity 16
quote_text: C,could it be… A love confession?!

name: Affinity 17
quote_text: Would you adventure with me to the ultimate dungeon?

name: Affinity 18
quote_text: My Charm works on both genders.

name: Affinity 19
quote_text: Dust, you're banned until you pay off all your debts!

name: Affinity 20
quote_text: I'm gonna be the number one succubus of the café!

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: Thank you for visiting!

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: I can help Vanir even more with this!

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: Gonna be so reliable if this goes on!

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: Looking forward to the next adventure!

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: Oh look, you've already become my slaves.

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: My goal is becoming the top succubus!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: Dream what you wanna dream, for a little money and vitality.

name: Misc 2
quote_text: As a succubus, it's a lifetime disgrace to let another woman take away your man!

name: Misc 3
quote_text: I am not a good attacker... But I'll support you all I can.

name: Misc 4
quote_text: I'm good at sneaking by someone's pillow.

name: Misc 5
quote_text: If only Vanir would pet my head…!

name: Misc 6
quote_text: Actually I'm older than you Dust, you know?

name: Misc 7
quote_text: If it is for Vanir, I'll gladly help anytime!

name: Misc 8
quote_text: God? Don't say that, it's bad luck!

name: Misc 9
quote_text: Wiz always gets scolded by Vanir. I'm jealous.

name: Misc 10
quote_text: The Axis Order is dangerous! Keep away from them!

name: Misc 11
quote_text: Yunyun is too honest it's almost worring.

name: Misc 12
quote_text: When sneaking into a big house, the first thing to do is to check if there are any barriers.

name: Greeting
quote_text: I'm Shadow. The one who hunts shadow within the shadows. Engrave my name in your hearts.

quote_text: If we can't see the deep darkness of the world, we're going to dig deeper... and deeper.

quote_text: Can we earn obtain skills with points? I wonder if it's more beneficial than obtaining skills at the end of training.

quote_text: I heard there was a spider-type fortress that can crawl the earth. The destroyer... It's truly a name that makes your heart pound.

quote_text: If you can, bring the sins of the entire world. I will take all of it with me.

quote_text: This is bad... Where can I buy under garments if there is no Mitsugoshi...?

quote_text: The desire to help someone precious to you. That has transformed me from be scared of fighting.

name: Affinity 14
quote_text: Uh... Lord Shadow is usually awesome, but I also want to see him as an adventurer...!

name: Affinity 15
quote_text: A silver-haired elf with blue eyes and a cute beauty mark is perfect to stay by Lord Shadow's side, right?

name: Level Up 1
quote_text: With this, I can be even more helpful to Lord Shadow...!

name: Level Up 2
quote_text: Hehe, I've gotten stronger.

name: Level Up 3
quote_text: This is... a new power...!

name: Level Up 4
quote_text: The skill has been enhanced.

name: Level Up 5
quote_text: Do you wish for an even greater power?

name: Level Up 6
quote_text: For the upcoming battle...!

name: Misc 1
quote_text: Aren't you interested in the new world that Lord Shadow will bring?

name: Misc 2
quote_text: With such determination... Shadow Garden will always welcome you.

name: Misc 3
quote_text: Did you call me?

name: Misc 4
quote_text: I have to live up to the expectation.

name: Misc 5
quote_text: Information can sometimes be a weapon. If you focus on every rumor of the town, it can be helpful.

name: Misc 6
quote_text: Does this bodysuit wonder you? It's very comfortable because it was originally made with slimes.

name: Misc 7
quote_text: We are the Shadow Garden. The one who hunts shadow within the shadows. A night without a moon... is dangerous.

name: Level Up 7
quote_text: I will carry out any kind of mission!

name: Level Up 8
quote_text: If it's for Lord Shadow...!

name: ASSET_CHARA_VOICE_304101059
quote_text: Ughh… It stinks…

name: ASSET_CHARA_VOICE_304102065
quote_text: Got any holy water? I want to get rid of this smell.

name: ASSET_CHARA_VOICE_304102068
quote_text: Our bond is strong! So can I give you a hug?

name: ASSET_CHARA_VOICE_304103072
quote_text: I always wanted to be covered in slime, it feels good.

name: ASSET_CHARA_VOICE_304103075
quote_text: Me all covered in slime… Is a turn on?!

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: I'm so happy you remembered my birthday. I'd love it if you did the same for Mia, though.

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: I never expected to be congratulated like this… Thank you.

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: Mwahaha! Today is Vanir Day! Join me and celebrate!

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: It's my birthday...? I don't feel any different, but I like the idea of celebrating with friends!

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: He said it was an "picture of awesome sister'! Hehe, he’s so cute!

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: Happy birthday, Dodonko. Here.

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: Happy birthday, Funifura… Did you get that from your brother?

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: I’m happy, thank you. I will be able to sleep anywhere with this.

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: Those who congratulate me are all fine people! Thank you!

name: Birthday Greeting
quote_text: Everyone in the Axis Order should be preparing for my birthday party by now.
